UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Marshal Maxwell laughs.>' WHERE `entry`=4223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I could have warned you, but what fun is that?' WHERE `entry`=4224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you spoken with John yet?' WHERE `entry`=4224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Where is he! I\'ll murder him!' WHERE `entry`=4241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='He\'s gone mad, apparently.$B$B<Maxwell lowers his head in mourning.>$B$BIt is unfortunate that a once proud and noble warrior would be turned into a blithering head case. I GUESS we\'ve reached a dead end...$B$BI must reward you for your efforts thus far, $N.' WHERE `entry`=4242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='As you look A-Me 01 over, you see two huge dents tarnishing what Karna obviously feels is a well-crafted piece of engineering. One dent decorates A-Me 01\'s shoulder, the other is on her head.$B$BNo power seems to be running through her components as you investigate further.' WHERE `entry`=4243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You remove the panel from A-Me 01\'s back yet again and carefully remove the old mithril casing that seems to have burnt out. The new one slides into place easily. The only thing left to do, assuming the mithril casing was the problem, is to flip the switch to the "Off" position, and then back to the "On" position.' WHERE `entry`=4244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, you\'ve done it! Wonderful! Thank you, $N.$B$BOh, my poor, A-Me. Look at all those dents. We\'ll get her up and running perfectly with just a little work.$B$BThank you again, $N. I really appreciate it.' WHERE `entry`=4245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you been able to help A-Me? That mithril casing you mentioned being destroyed was a good guess at what was wrong. I\'m sure if you replace that, she\'ll reactivate and be able to come home.' WHERE `entry`=4245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes, s, $N. Felwood has been through much hardship. Thank you for what you have done.$B$BOne day, we may be able to reclaim Felwood from the corruption; every kind deed helps.' WHERE `entry`=4261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh dear! Are you sure Incendius said \'Ragnaros?\'$B$B<Jalinda hands you something and pats you on the wrist as she fades deep into thought.>' WHERE `entry`=4263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Marshal Windsor takes the note and begins reading.>' WHERE `entry`=4264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome home, $N. Raschal checked in just a little while ago and told me what happened.$B$BI... no, the entire Stronghold can\'t even begin to thank you for your great deed; Raschal would have been dead without your timely aid, and your assistance came to us without even so much as the whisper of a mercenary\'s fee. You bear the mark of a true hero. Know that you will always have a friend in Ginro Hearthkindle.' WHERE `entry`=4265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You have something to report, $N?' WHERE `entry`=4265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N, I give you my warmest thanks for the aid you\'ve given us. Your bravery in the face of overwhelming odds has warranted a reward worth a thousand times greater. Nevertheless, I hope you accept this on behalf of the entire Stronghold.$B$BNow, if I may... I\'d like to ask for your aid one more time. In light of the discovery of the Zukk\'ash hive here in Feralas, I think you\'re the best choice for this mission.' WHERE `entry`=4266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We night elves know of the terror outlined in this report. Shandris was wise to send this, and you, to me.$B$BThese creatures will consume Feralas rapidly; they are nothing short of one of the greatest menaces we all will ever face. The insects you and the courier encountered are known as the silithid. They are mere tools of one of the greatest threats that both the Horde and Alliance will ever face.$B$BI pray we will have the resolve to defeat them before they destroy us.' WHERE `entry`=4267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Elune be praised, the delivery from Feathermoon Stronghold has finally arrived!$B$BYour presence here indicates to me that perhaps some ill fate may have befallen Raschal, our usual courier. I hope that everything works out. I know that recently, the Woodpaw have become highly agitated from some source to their south. Maybe he fell to the wilds there; I would be careful, friend.$B$BRegardless, thank you again. Here is payment for this parcel\'s delivery.' WHERE `entry`=4281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Marshal Windsor snatches the two tablets from your hands.>$B$BWe need to get out of here!' WHERE `entry`=4282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done it! Your reward is: RUB MY BELLY! GO ON! RUB IT!' WHERE `entry`=4283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I know the stories are true, $N.' WHERE `entry`=4285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you visited the pylon, $N?' WHERE `entry`=4285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Oralius starts rummaging through the mountainous pile of fanny packs.>$B$BOH WONDERFUL!$B$B<Oralius sticks his large nose into the pile and takes a whiff.>$B$BDELICIOUS! Look at all these goodies!$B$BTake one for yourself, $N. There\'s plenty to go around.' WHERE `entry`=4286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Un\'Goro is such a strange place, $N. When you enter the crater, it\'s as if you are in a completely different world...' WHERE `entry`=4287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you visited the pylon, $N?' WHERE `entry`=4287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='There are many hidden areas of the crater along the sides. Try exploring the winding paths if you can\'t think of anywhere else to look, $N.' WHERE `entry`=4288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you visited the pylon, $N?' WHERE `entry`=4288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So, you have proven strong, strong enough to best the great apes of Un\'Goro--that is good. The challenge was small compared to Lar\'korwi, but I will not take such a great victory away from you.$B$BThese pelts will make wonderful clothing for my tribe. You have helped me and proven worthy.$B$BBefore you set off on another task, let us give praise to the Earth Mother and thank the spirits of those apes you killed--they must know their deaths will not be wasted.' WHERE `entry`=4289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This will do nicely, $N. It seems Lar\'korwi eats well these days. Although, I wonder where he found a threshadon in this area. Odd.$B$BRegardless, I will hold onto this until you are ready for your confrontation with the beast. Do not worry for my safety--I am sure you\'ve angered Lar\'korwi enough that he will not kill me until after he\'s tasted your flesh.' WHERE `entry`=4290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, fine specimens, $N. The two pieces you\'ve found should be perfect for baiting Lar\'korwi into the open. I cannot wait to see the outcome of your fight with the monster. He is a massive thing with claws as sharp as the finest blades. You will look into his eyes and you will know death.' WHERE `entry`=4291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Earth Mother be praised! You\'ve done it! Fair play to you, $N. You have proven to be a great $C in your own right. Your spirit is strong. Your bravery unmatched. And your strength has been fortified. I bow down to your skills.$B$BOnly the greatest of my ancestors could have accomplished something so incredible. Congratulations.' WHERE `entry`=4292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, excellent. These samples will do nicely. I thank you for your help.$B$BOnce we\'ve gathered all the samples of slimes, we\'ll be able to determine more. I am beginning to suspect that Lady Sylvanas\' hunch was not only correct, but more insightful than even she could have predicted. These samples are very interesting. Just seeing how they\'ve reacted with my compounds... hmm, yes, we\'ll definitely need to investigate further.' WHERE `entry`=4293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Truly amazing, $N. This Un\'Goro Crater is holding many more secrets than I expected. I wonder what else we will discover as we test further.$B$BSimply amazing... look at the purity of these samples. Hmm, I wonder what it could mean. They seem to be elemental in nature, but... something more. They remind me of... of the Old Gods. We\'ve found traces of them throughout Azeroth, and now I wonder if these creatures aren\'t related to them somehow.$B$BWe shall have to test further.' WHERE `entry`=4294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='What\'s this?  Ah!  It smells like Dark Iron Ale!  Drink has blurred my sight, but I can tell that you, sir, are a real friend!' WHERE `entry`=4295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, you found the tablet! And your transcription is superb! Are you sure you\'re a $C and not a scribe?$B$BHere you are, $N. Here is the payment I promised.' WHERE `entry`=4296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These\'ll do nicely, and if I\'m not mistaken, your little egg\'s just about ready to hatch. How does it feel? You know, you about to be a father? Haha, didn\'t think ya\'d have to deal with such responsibility, now did ya?' WHERE `entry`=4297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Here, take the egg... better you have it so it bonds to you and looks to you to be its dadda.$B$BCongrats, $N. You\'re a parent... kinda.' WHERE `entry`=4298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, these do nicely. Thank you, $N. An\' you be here long before they needed... that be good.$B$BMaybe we have a weapon fashioned for you from the claws. What do you say?' WHERE `entry`=4300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. I am pleased. You have done a great thing here today.$B$BU\'cha was one of the greatest apes I had ever seen. The fact that you have bested his strength speaks well of your own strength... and courage.$B$BIt is only fitting that I give you this as a sign of respect. You have earned it.' WHERE `entry`=4301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Alright, $N. This is fascinating... I can only hope that my diagrams are correct! I compiled everything into this manual, which you can have.$B$BI believe I can answer any questions you have about the crystals now, $N.' WHERE `entry`=4321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Amazing, $N. Simply amazing. Windsor stormed through here not five minutes ago. He makes some grand claims but purports that they are supported by his evidence. He is on his way to Stormwind now to confront Bolvar and ... Lady Prestor.' WHERE `entry`=4322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You look exhausted, $N. Perhaps you should have a seat by the fire and relax.' WHERE `entry`=4322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes, I\'m looking for my brother. We must find him and retrieve him, bless his heart.$B$BBut if we can\'t bring all of him... then his head will suffice.' WHERE `entry`=4324;
