UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done well! That\'s less Templars for me to worry about.$B$BHere you go, $N. Hope there\'s something useful in there for you.' WHERE `entry`=8362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent, $N!  Defeating those Dukes will leave the Twilight\'s Hammer reeling for a while. As promised, here\'s your reward. It\'s some of the better stuff Huum and I have found.' WHERE `entry`=8363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I knew you\'d come through, $N! Here\'s your reward.' WHERE `entry`=8364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh you\'re a darling, even if it did take you longer than I am accustomed to. This shipment should make me quite a bit of money once I\'ve cleaned and personalized these hats. And seeing as I\'m always willing to reward work that\'s well done, here\'s a little something for you. I suggest that you spend some of it on a bath sweetie.' WHERE `entry`=8365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N! You are the man!!!$B$BI\'m sure that the Cartel will ease up on me now that you\'ve dealt with those Southsea scum. Let\'s see, what can I give you as a reward? How about a little coin and you choose from one of these for your trouble?' WHERE `entry`=8366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your trials have not been easy, but your courage did not escape you and your strength did not fail. Part with past tokens of victory, $C. None shall need them as a reminder of your worth. Stand up straight, $N. Today you will walk with great pride for you are a hero!' WHERE `entry`=8367;
