UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Here you go, here you go!  A prize fit for a king!  Congratulations to you, my friend!$B$BIf you have more tickets you\'d like to turn in, then please let me know!  For as long as the Darkmoon Faire is here, I\'ll redeem your tickets.' WHERE `entry`=9249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The archmages have died.$B$BDo not mourn their passing, $N. All such things are fated. Just as you holding the staff of the Guardian was fated...' WHERE `entry`=9250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='There is a being within... a being not of this world.' WHERE `entry`=9251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Many thanks, $N. Our job is a thankless one, but today you helped make it a bit easier.' WHERE `entry`=9252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You must\'ve been sent by someone at Fairbreeze Village. I knew it would just be a matter of time until help arrived.' WHERE `entry`=9253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s so nice of my old mentor to check on me. It\'s too bad she lost faith in my research long ago.$B$BDon\'t waste your time trying to get me to return to her; you can either help me with my research or leave.' WHERE `entry`=9254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These notes... are shocking. If they\'re correct it means the damage to the land on the Dead Scar is irreversible.$B$BI\'ll notify the grand magister right away. More reason for our race to escape this world and find our true fate in Outland.' WHERE `entry`=9255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thanks for coming, $N. Things are worse than we had anticipated. The Wretched have taken over Sunsail Anchorage in its entirety.' WHERE `entry`=9256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, my brother sent you. I do have a task I could use assistance with.' WHERE `entry`=9258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let us observe a minute of silence for our fallen mates, $N.$B$B<The Bloodsail Traitor grins at you and winks.>$B$BBeing a traitor is one thing, murdering yer own buckos... that\'d be just downright despicable, aye!' WHERE `entry`=9259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $N. You\'re on a quick path to redeeming yourself with our fair town.' WHERE `entry`=9266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m happy you\'re seeing the error of your ways, $N. Keep the supplies coming; we\'re not going to forget about you so easily, $Gmister:miss;!' WHERE `entry`=9267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Keep it coming, $N. Us goblins don\'t forget that easily!' WHERE `entry`=9268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yarrr... if ye be keen on enjoying the company of us experienced sea dogs, you\'d best belay dressing like a blaggard! Here, put on something proper \'fore I keelhaul yer hide.$B$BThese\'ll fit ye better than they ever fit that old dog, Red-Eyed Ben. Lost him in a devil of a storm at sea.$B$BWear \'em with pride, mate!' WHERE `entry`=9272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='Welcome to the World of Warcraft!$B$BAs special thanks for purchasing the World of Warcraft Collector\'s Edition, turn in this gift voucher to Jaeleil at the Crash Site in Ammen Vale. You\'ll then be given a gift: a little companion to join you on your quest for adventure and glory.$B$BThanks again, and enjoy your stay in the World of Warcraft!',`objectives_loc8`='Bring the Ammen Vale Gift Voucher to Jaeleil inside the ship at the Crash Site in Ammen Vale.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You are indeed a special hero, $N. We welcome you to the world of Azeroth, and offer you one of these unique gifts!' WHERE `entry`=9278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N. by my eternal soul, it is good to see you! I don\'t know why the Exodar crashed. Only those of us that were in this part of the ship remain.$B$BThere\'s not much time if we\'re to save everyone that we can!' WHERE `entry`=9279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Regrettable that those creatures had to die so that we might live - indiscriminate killing is not the $R way. However, the blood you gathered will replenish our healing crystals, so their deaths will not be in vain.' WHERE `entry`=9280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Kaendris sent you? I might have a task for you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=9282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Light be praised! You\'ve done what only a true heroine could have done, $N! The draenei you saved owes their continued life to your selflessness!$B$BPlease, take this supply pouch. You look like you can use it more than I.' WHERE `entry`=9283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m glad that you have come to me. For quite some time now I have been responsible for the training of our young $Cs, a responsibility that I intend to continue on this new world. I\'ve had my eye upon you for a while now and it would be my honor to help train you in the ways of the $C.$BShall we begin?' WHERE `entry`=9288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is good that you seek my guidance. For centuries I have taught young $R warriors, so I may know a thing or two on how you should begin. I see in you the makings of a great $C, but only if you listen carefully to what I have to teach.$B$BAre you ready to learn, young $C?' WHERE `entry`=9289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am pleased that you have come seeking my knowledge. We have much to do if your magical skills are to be honed. For over a hundred years I have taught the arcane, frost and fire magics, and I can feel them just as strongly on this world. Would you like me to impart some of what I know to you?' WHERE `entry`=9290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It gives me great hope for our future that you come seeking my wisdom. While I have my hands full here with our injured, I am not so busy that I cannot spare a moment to aid you in your first steps as a $C. To walk in the Light is the highest of callings, and one that I am certain you are more than ready to undertake! Speak with me again when you feel that you are ready to begin your training.' WHERE `entry`=9291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='With many of the owlkin now inoculated. we can focus on getting out of here and not have to worry about wiping out the owlkin population in the area.$B$BHere. choose from these. You\'ve done good work. and you deserve to be rewarded!' WHERE `entry`=9303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The more we can do to clear up Nestlewood. the faster Zhanaa can get back to work.' WHERE `entry`=9303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Help... blood elves! They... ambushed... me. Don\'t have... long.' WHERE `entry`=9309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I got it. I got it! I think I managed to fix the emitter! Here, I\'ll just activate this last crystal and that should do it.$B$BTake a look at the emitter, $N. It looks like it\'s beginning to work... someone is appearing!' WHERE `entry`=9312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, good to see you again! I\'m glad that we were both able to get our emitters fixed or we might never have found one another. And don\'t worry, we\'ll see to it that Ammen Vale gets help and supplies.$B$BSpeaking of assistance, now that you\'re here, go around and introduce yourself to the others. I know that there\'s plenty to do.' WHERE `entry`=9313;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I apologize for the shoddy intelligence. $C. Had I known of this Anok\'suten ahead of time, I surely would have told you.$B$BWe\'re spread too thin and things are slipping through the cracks!' WHERE `entry`=9315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have proven that you are not entirely useless, mortal.' WHERE `entry`=9319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you found your way through the dark?' WHERE `entry`=9319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your spirit glows with the warmth of the Kalimdor fires, friend. Is the heat not invigorating? Once the power fades from you, perhaps these will help rekindle the feeling.' WHERE `entry`=9322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, here you are. A little wearier, a bit dustier, but enlightened! The heat touches us all during this season and unites us; your very being glows with the power of the fires you touched. Ah, but these days enlightenment is taken as a rather poor reward for being sent on a task, I suppose. Take these, then, and enjoy the celebration.' WHERE `entry`=9323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='What\'s this? Unless I\'m mistaken, this flame has been taken from the heart of Orgrimmar itself! The fierce hearts of the orcs and trolls are reflected in its searing heat. What a fine addition to our collection--how brave you are, stealing into the enemy\'s lair to retrieve the sacred flame!' WHERE `entry`=9324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Unless I miss my guess, this fire has been taken from the cliffs of Thunder Bluff! How it sings with the power of the spirits! You are quite the thief, $N. Take this as just payment for your skill. Now, if only we had the flames of all three cities...' WHERE `entry`=9325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hm... what a strange fire! It is subdued, nearly smoldering, but the heat is intense. And you received this from the Undercity, you say? Fascinating. With the flames of all three cities, who knows what we could accomplish?' WHERE `entry`=9326;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='And this brightly-burning fire... you say it came from Stormwind? Remarkable! That must have been quite an adventure! I\'ll pay you for this, of course. If you find anything else like this, be sure to speak with me again.' WHERE `entry`=9330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This hearty flame must be from the halls of Ironforge; it\'s as stalwart as the dwarves themselves. A fine catch, $N. If I had the fires of the other cities... ah, but never mind. Here is your payment.' WHERE `entry`=9331;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This fire aches of ancient sorrow, $N. You pulled this from the roots of Teldrassil, you say? Fascinating! Here is a reward for your skill. Return to me should you find anything else like this; I may have a use for it.' WHERE `entry`=9332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You honor us, $N. With your continued efforts we will overcome all obstacles.' WHERE `entry`=9338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve proven yourself, today, $N.$B$BWhile I have little else to give you, I do have this crown; a fitting gift for a conqueror. May it light your way.' WHERE `entry`=9339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you for your help, $N. Got anything up your sleeve to make the peons earn their keep?' WHERE `entry`=9342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Night elves? Here? Those rats!$B$BDo you suppose they had anything to do with the malfunction in my sanctum? If you have any information, you\'d better take it to Captain Sunbrand at once!' WHERE `entry`=9352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you uncovered anything? Are the night elves behind this?' WHERE `entry`=9352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'re here to help us? Why didn\'t you say so earlier? We can always use a hand!' WHERE `entry`=9358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'re here to help? Excellent!$B$BThe battle against the Amani trolls has taken its toll on us and capable fighters such as yourself are always welcome.' WHERE `entry`=9359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The trolls have been keeping us pinned here while planning an attack on Fairbreeze Village. We were not expecting this at all.' WHERE `entry`=9360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I must say, this shell has a strange aura. It seems only fitting that part of your reward for retrieving it would be to test its magical capabilities...' WHERE `entry`=9362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Splendid! Splendid!$B$BNow we are able to reform this magic into a new spell. Behold!' WHERE `entry`=9364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve proven yourself, today, $N.$B$BWhile I have little else to give you, I do have this crown; a fitting gift for a conqueror. May it light your way.' WHERE `entry`=9365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! It seems we\'ve appointed dutiful Flamekeepers this year if the bonfires are as well-kept as you claim. Thank you for inspecting them for me; here, take this as a small token of my esteem.' WHERE `entry`=9367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent work, $N. With the shadows destroyed, it can only be a matter of time before the Lich King decides to recall his necropolises and leave us in peace.' WHERE `entry`=9368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Regrettable that those creatures had to die so that we might live - indiscriminate killing is not the draenei way. However, the blood you gathered will replenish our healing crystals, so their deaths will not be in vain.' WHERE `entry`=9369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Taleris shouts to several of the blood elves at the outpost.>$B$BGet her inside and see to her wounds!$B$B<Taleris turns back to you.>$B$BShe\'s fortunate that you found her when you did, $C. I don\'t think she\'d have lasted much longer out there.$B$BCan you make out what she was saying?' WHERE `entry`=9375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have proven that you are not entirely useless, mortal.' WHERE `entry`=9386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you found your way through the dark?' WHERE `entry`=9386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ahhh, so they do still burn. I am glad; it would not do for those fires to burn out before their time. You have done well, $N. Take this with my blessing.' WHERE `entry`=9388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you\'ve returned, and you\'ve seen to the emerald flames of the continent. What do you think, mm? A rare and wonderful sight, to be certain. I am aware, however, that tangible rewards are better appreciated... so please, take this for your trouble.' WHERE `entry`=9389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve found the body of a young draenei $C. He appears to have been slain by a blow to his back.' WHERE `entry`=9390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, good of Magistrix Dawnstrider to finally respond to my simple requests. I should take up the matter of her attitude with the regent lord in Silvermoon. She\'s quite rude!$B$BNothing for you to concern yourself with though. Now that you\'re here, maybe I\'ll finally be able to get those party supplies that I\'ve been waiting for?' WHERE `entry`=9395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The corpse matches the description of Krun Spinebreaker, Hellfire Citadel\'s assassin. As you turn the body over, you notice a stone axe protruding from his back.' WHERE `entry`=9400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='He was killed by this weapon?  It can\'t be!$B$BHave we... found them?' WHERE `entry`=9401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, well done... I told you to jump in a pond, and you did. I can only imagine what you\'d do if one of your good friends asked it of you.$B$BIf you want a reward for your efforts, it is this: never lift a finger without first knowing what\'s in it for you. The $C\'s mind is his greatest weapon. Remember that and try to use yours a bit more.' WHERE `entry`=9402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let\'s see what you\'ve brought me...$B$B<He holds the phial up to the light and examines it closely.>$B$BYes, this will do. Well done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done as I\'ve asked, $N, and you may take your reward now.' WHERE `entry`=9404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I understand Nazgrel\'s request, $C. Say no more.' WHERE `entry`=9405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Alliance needs every able body they can get. The Horde has been receiving a steady supply of reinforcements from the northern part of the continent, and it\'s been a struggle to keep up.$B$BLet me explain the situation to you.' WHERE `entry`=9415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s good that you\'re here, but there\'s no time to waste making small talk. You need instructions, and then you need to get out there.$B$BListen up.' WHERE `entry`=9416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Be careful out there, but also be quick. We have no time to lose.' WHERE `entry`=9419;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You did your part. I guess a deal is a deal! $B$BHere you go. friend. Treat it well.' WHERE `entry`=9420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am Firmanvaar and you are wise to seek me out. It is my calling to provide instruction to $C, especially those who are just beginning to learn.$B$BShamanism is only now being relearned amongst the $R, $N. You are brave to follow its path as it is not popular amongst your kind.$B$BI will be here when you feel you are ready for further training.' WHERE `entry`=9421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done well, $N. These resources will be added to our stockpiles, and every bit is to our gain and our enemy\'s loss.' WHERE `entry`=9422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Be wary of the dangers of the desert, $N. With the Alliance lurking in the dunes, any step could be your last.' WHERE `entry`=9422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Sedai, dear brother...$B$BThose cowardly orcs! He was unarmed, how could they?$B$BLeave me be, $N. I thank you for your assistance but I wish to be alone with my thoughts now.' WHERE `entry`=9423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes. I feel the fel presence in the pools weakening.$B$BYou\'ve done well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You return, $N. Are the waters cleansed?' WHERE `entry`=9427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The ambassador sent word ahead, so I\'ve been expecting you.$B$BThe ambassador simply wants you to do as much as you can to help out around here. She said something about making sure to cement our relationship with the rest of the Horde.$B$BAsk around - there are others in need of help further back in the Post. And I hear that there\'s another Horde outpost called Zoram\'gar Outpost on the coast all the way to the west.' WHERE `entry`=9428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank the Light! From the tone of the foreman\'s letter, it sounded as if that box of crystals contained the only known samples from the mine. If we had lost them, $N, we may never have seen another like them.$B$BI can\'t thank you enough for your help.' WHERE `entry`=9435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N! As soon as Ithania has had time to rest and my preparations are complete, we\'ll depart this sodden wasteland and head back to civilization.' WHERE `entry`=9437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you freed Ithania and reclaimed my cargo from those glorified privateers?' WHERE `entry`=9437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'re a miracle worker, $N! I tell you, I\'ve never been so eager for a change of clothes in my life.$B$BAnd my rapier! I felt positively naked without my blade.$B$BYou are to be commended and rewarded for your efforts. Never let it be said that Sarophas failed to acknowledge the little people who\'ve helped him along the way!' WHERE `entry`=9439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It means very much to us that you come to aid us in our time of need. We\'ll not easily forget you nor he who sends you.$B$BYou have our thanks.' WHERE `entry`=9441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Gorkan said good things about you. They\'re all turning out to be true.$B$BThanks for your help.' WHERE `entry`=9442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The first step is complete. Hand me the Mark of the Lightbringer and I will transform it into something more suitable.$B$BThen my revenge will begin in earnest, $C!' WHERE `entry`=9443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Forgives me?  He FORGIVES ME?!!!$B$BI don\'t care what that old ghost had to say - it was his fault!  Everything that\'s happened to Quel\'Thalas was a result of his incompetence!$B$BIt is clear that the defiling did not work. Go, be gone from my sight!  I must think this through.' WHERE `entry`=9444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='It is done, then?  Uther\'s Tomb is defiled?' WHERE `entry`=9444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Lightbringer appeared before you? That is amazing! And you made it all possible through your selfless help to the anchorite.$B$BIf even half of the stories are to be believed, Uther was a great man. And, like him, you are a true hero to all of the good people of Azeroth, $N!' WHERE `entry`=9446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Aren\'t you supposed to be walking to Uther\'s Tomb with Anchorite Truuen?' WHERE `entry`=9446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='May the spirits bless you, $N. The Mag\'har are in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=9447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You\'ve returned, $N. Is your task complete?' WHERE `entry`=9447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is done then. I thank you for showing your compassion. Once corrupted by whatever Cersei was feeding them, there is nothing else that could be done.$B$BThey are now at peace and hopefully my studies of the others will bear fruit so that they can be rehabilitated.' WHERE `entry`=9448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You are bold to seek my wisdom after what your people have done to these islands, stranger! Still, there is much to be said for your bravery, so I will impart to you some knowledge.$B$BThe earth beneath your feet forms the foundation for all things. The sky, the waters, even great fire - all rest upon its shoulders. While those others often form chaotic tempests, the earth abides. It grants strength and fortitude to the core of your being.' WHERE `entry`=9449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have done well. By thinning out the restless spirits you have helped to heal the imbalance between the elements, which your people inadvertently caused.$B$BThroughout your journey as a $C you must keep this in mind when calling upon our power. The balance must be preserved.' WHERE `entry`=9450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have done well, $N. In helping to restore the balance of the elements at the grove, you have also created a balance between the earth element of this world and the $R. Perhaps this will help to bring understanding to those amongst us who do not approve of our ways?$B$BI will create for you a totem through which you will be able to call on the power of earth to do your bidding. And with time, more of the mysteries of earth will be revealed to you.$B$BNow, take your totem, $C.' WHERE `entry`=9451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='How did such a thing end up in the stomach of a nightstalker? Could the debris from the crash have contaminated more beasts?' WHERE `entry`=9455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent!  Such a personal item carries a strong scent of the intruders--enough to guide Whisper into their ranks...' WHERE `entry`=9460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hello, $N, I have been expecting you. I trust this day finds you well?' WHERE `entry`=9461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Just in time, $N. I hope you are ready to continue your training. This next task will be a difficult one.' WHERE `entry`=9462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I trust that the burning I see behind your eyes is from a desire to grow and understand?  Good!$B$BTuluun has sent you here because he sees your potential to both learn and help with a problem that the crash of your Exodar has caused.$B$BWe shall see.' WHERE `entry`=9464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='See how its fire never goes out?  That is the work of Hauteur. It is a symbol of his arrogance. Flame is meant to consume that which it burns and then itself die, to be reborn anew another time.$B$BI would help you douse the torch, but it must stay lit for you to deal with Hauteur. We will let it burn a little while longer.' WHERE `entry`=9465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is a valuable lesson that you learn here today. It is the story of endings and new beginnings.$B$BWhen first we spoke I told you that fire was not just destruction, but also a renewing force of the elements. Through your actions you have both destroyed and saved Hauteur, for he shall be reborn from his ashes.' WHERE `entry`=9467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have passed through the cleansing fire of destruction and been renewed, $N. This is not unlike the tribulation the $R people are currently undergoing. And through saving Hauteur from himself, you have secured your connection to the elemental fire of this world.' WHERE `entry`=9468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Well, $N. Is it done?' WHERE `entry`=9472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You know, maybe we can become friends after all. Follow me; we don\'t want to have to share this with the others now, do we?' WHERE `entry`=9483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Withstanding the numerous claws and bites from the dragonhawk is a sign of your tenacity. Do you have the strength to learn more?' WHERE `entry`=9484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you mastered the dragonhawk?' WHERE `entry`=9484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you see $N, there is nothing left for me to teach you at this time. You already understand what it is to befriend those you once hunted. You need only to choose one of nature\'s allies with traits that match your own.' WHERE `entry`=9485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you mastered the mistbat?' WHERE `entry`=9485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have shown both strength and tenacity. There remains the final test until you can tame without the use of magic.' WHERE `entry`=9486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you hunted alongside the springpaw?' WHERE `entry`=9486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Such a waste, using magic to construct beings of physical strength. I always thought that\'s why we allied with the lesser races, after all.$B$BYou were good to destroy them so we can use what remains for a more suitable purpose.' WHERE `entry`=9487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You really don\'t need to know the intricacies of crafting a magical robe, $N, you just need to know what to bring me.$B$BAnd let me be honest, you brought enough for several robes. The profit I\'ll make should more than cover the costs to make your robe, and even enough to buy myself something nice. Looks like the thanks belong to you!' WHERE `entry`=9488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Already the rangers speak of your blessings with awe and respect. Now you can see how the Light serves us, allowing us to help others, but only after we have helped ourselves.' WHERE `entry`=9489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you given hope where it waned?' WHERE `entry`=9489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is the ring, is it? Not much to look at, but you know what they say about one elves\' trash...$B$BAnd let\'s not forget your payment. Don\'t feel shy about spending it right here sister!' WHERE `entry`=9491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. With your victory in Hellfire Citadel, we have struck a major blow against the orcs.$B$BI must speak with Field Commander Romus about following up and ensuring that the orcs stay on the defensive. Now that we\'ve been reinforced, we can do far more than simply defend Honor Hold.' WHERE `entry`=9492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That is excellent news, indeed, $N. With progress to report from Hellfire Citadel, perhaps we can afford to turn our attention to the Fel Horde presence other parts of the peninsula and Outland as a whole.' WHERE `entry`=9493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done! I can\'t hope to replicate the feats of Grand Warlock Nethekurse, nor should I aspire to, but we would be fools to ignore the power of the fel embers.$B$BHowever, there are those who would forbid the type of research I\'m about to embark upon, and for that reason, I must keep my efforts secret. Please do not speak of this to anyone, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have done well, $N. In his prime, Kargath Bladefist was a fine warrior, a hero and example to his people.$B$BHis death is a blow to us all, but especially to Warchief Thrall. Whatever happened to him in his final days, we should not forget the orc Kargath once was, nor the lessons to be learned from his downfall.$B$BFor your service to the Horde, $N, you are to be rewarded with your choice from among these weapons.' WHERE `entry`=9495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent job, $N. With the legionnaires broken, it will be easier to face the Fel Horde on the battlefield, though they remain a formidable enemy.' WHERE `entry`=9496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome to Falcon Watch, $R. All our Horde allies are welcome here, especially those recommended by Martik.' WHERE `entry`=9498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome to Falcon Watch, $Gbrother:sister;. Many other blood elves haven\'t been fortunate enough to make it this far.$B$BIt\'s a terrible shame; our work in Outland has just begun.' WHERE `entry`=9499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We meet again. I have been watching your progress from afar, $C, and I am pleased.$B$BThe time has come for you to commune with the element of water, to learn its mysteries and give yourself over to the water so that you might in turn learn to master it.' WHERE `entry`=9500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Do not fear, $N. While you are here we will speak using our minds.$B$BI am grateful to Farseer Nobundo for sending you to me. There is a great disturbance that is polluting the waters on and around Bloodmyst Isle. Not even the blind would fail to notice the effect this is having on its creatures and the environment.$B$BYou and I will work together to stop this corruption before it spreads further.' WHERE `entry`=9501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We meet again. I have been watching your progress from afar, $C, and I am pleased.$B$BThe time has come for you to commune with the element of water, to learn its mysteries and give yourself over to the water so that you might in turn learn to master it.' WHERE `entry`=9502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $C. These should be enough so that I can examine this corruption. Then we will have a better idea of how to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=9503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='It is worse than I feared. The corruption is very potent and if unchecked it could spread to the ocean currents and be carried throughout all of Azeroth!$B$BWe are going to need a sample of the purest water to counter this malignancy. There is a forest on the nearby continent of Kalimdor named Ashenvale. Near its southwestern border is a place called the Ruins of Stardust.$B$BTake this bota bag and fill it with the water from the fountain on the small island at the center of the ruins. Hurry, $N!',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Water parts easily, yet put enough of it together and it will create an unstoppable force. It washes away earth and fire, and easily pushes air out of the way.$B$BWe are that unstoppable force, $N, not those that have poisoned Bloodmyst Isle!' WHERE `entry`=9504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is done then!  The crisis is averted and you have put in motion the restoration of the water on Bloodmyst Isle. Over time, the water, in conjunction with the other elements, will heal itself.$B$BIt is unfortunate that the blood elves cannot see that by contaminating their surroundings they\'re killing themselves off as well!' WHERE `entry`=9508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have comported yourself with wisdom beyond your years, $N. I can sense that the water element is pleased with your actions. It will be my great honor to take the pure water that you bear and combine its essence into your new water totem.$B$BRemember well the lessons of water as you go forward and you will gain an even greater understanding and mastery of the element.' WHERE `entry`=9509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Bless yer heart. stranger. This\'ll go a long ways in liftin\' the morale o\' the crew.' WHERE `entry`=9512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='My pappy would be proud! His boy strikes it big at the first set of night elf ruins he comes across... With your help, of course. Yes, don\'t worry, I won\'t leave you out of the discovery. You\'re a $R, right? Right, sure... $R. They\'ll learn all about you in Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=9523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I thank you, $N. I must admit I didn\'t expect a rescue party to be on its way.$B$BI will round up the remaining prisoners and lead them back to Honor Hold.' WHERE `entry`=9524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve brightened my day, $C. When I die, I will make sure it\'s in the battlefield... covered in the blood of my opponents and taking them down with me.' WHERE `entry`=9525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Surely you have not yet planted all of my seeds?' WHERE `entry`=9526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Tears of joy stream down Cowlen\'s face.>$B$BHow can I ever repay you for this, $N? Please, take this heirloom. It symbolizes a sacred bond of friendship, trust and love amongst night elves. You are a $Gbrother:sister; to me - from this day until the end of time...' WHERE `entry`=9528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='As you gaze into the stone, your vision begins to swirl...' WHERE `entry`=9529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I hope you can see I am deep under cover... at least I was.' WHERE `entry`=9532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill Gorgannon and Diathorus the Seeker, and then return to Velusha at Splintertree Post in Ashenvale.' WHERE `entry`=9536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Can I offer you any assistance, $N? You sound troubled.' WHERE `entry`=9543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The prophecy spoke of one that would rise and deliver us from the oppressive grasp of Bristlelimb -- that the spirits themselves would herald the arrival of this hero.$B$BAnd now, you have come.$B$BI humble myself before you, great one.' WHERE `entry`=9544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='[Furbolg] So the prophecy of Akida is true... A hero has been delivered to us.' WHERE `entry`=9544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='And finally we come to it, the last of the four great elements: air. Do you think yourself wise enough to continue, $N?' WHERE `entry`=9547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='And finally we come to it, the last of the four great elements: air. Do you think yourself wise enough to continue, $N?' WHERE `entry`=9551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It was whispered to me on the winds that you would be coming, $C.$B$BFarseer Nobundo thinks very highly of you, and from what I have heard of your travels, so do I.' WHERE `entry`=9552;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I have been awaiting your arrival, $C. You come seeking wisdom, and something else I sense.$B$BVery well, let us begin.' WHERE `entry`=9553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am proud of you, $N. You have persevered where others falter, and in the process you\'ve gained a greater understanding of the elements and yourself. Remember their lessons as you go through life and you will be the wiser for it.$B$BNow, hand me the whorl from Susurrus so that I may imbue it into your air totem. As with the other totems, it will serve as both a focus and a reminder of the connection that you have forged with the elements.' WHERE `entry`=9554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Greetings. It is always heartening to meet a $R who is open to the way of shamanism. There are so few.$B$BYou have learned not to judge the flame for its outward appearance, just as you should not judge mine.$B$BYou are here because you are ready to create your fire totem.' WHERE `entry`=9555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Mmmmm... Delicious grain... Parkat will be delighted!' WHERE `entry`=9562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Why. yes! You seem to be quite an OK $R. I suppose I can trust you.' WHERE `entry`=9563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s a good start. With those three dead their forces should be in disarray. And with their artillery up there silenced we\'ll have an easier time getting close enough to take the citadel!$B$BBut there\'s more to this than meets the eye - I can feel it - so I\'m going to have something else for you to do.$B$BFor the time being, though, you\'ve done well. Take your pick of any of these from the Thrallmar armory.' WHERE `entry`=9572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Do you know what I hate worse than being wrong? Losing gold on a bet that you couldn\'t pull it off, sweetheart.$B$BOutstanding! With those three dead their forces should be in disarray. And with their artillery up there silenced we\'ll have an easier time getting close enough to take the citadel!$B$BI have a feeling there\'s more to this than meets the eye, though' WHERE `entry`=9575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Ruada nods solemnly.>$B$BThen it is done.$B$BYou are ready for your next lesson, $N, but I will not be the one to teach it to you.' WHERE `entry`=9582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you for helping Tavara. So many are unfamiliar with these lands and find trouble where they least expect.$B$BIt would honor me if you were to wear these robes. They mark you as one of the protectors of Azure Watch and a devout follower of the Light.' WHERE `entry`=9586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you found Tavara?' WHERE `entry`=9586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s signed by Illidan you say?! Let me have that.$B$B<Nazgrel reads the letter, and then again a second time, thinking a moment before going on.>$B$BThis news that you bring is ominous indeed. Knowing this, we must accelerate our plans against Hellfire Citadel and this Blood Furnace. Because you have shown that you can get the job done, I want you to head up those plans!$B$BCenturion Caza\'rez will give you your next mission, though I suspect it will be far deadlier than your first.$B$BLok\'tar ogar, $N!' WHERE `entry`=9588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am impressed with your abilities, $N. Not once, but twice now you have infiltrated Hellfire Citadel for us and accomplished what was asked of you.$B$BI will see to it that this blood is delivered to those who can unlock its mysteries. Who knows, perhaps we can find a way to reverse the process?' WHERE `entry`=9590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m sure the first thing you learned was how unsympathetic the crawler was during the bonding process. It\'s all claws until they know you aren\'t there to throw them into a boiling pot.' WHERE `entry`=9591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Were you able to harness the magic of the totem to befriend a barbed crawler?  They are feisty little creatures!' WHERE `entry`=9591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Looks like the timberstrider didn\'t peck your eyes out.$B$B<Kella looks away for a moment.>$B$BNot that I thought that would happen, of course!' WHERE `entry`=9592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The timberstrider is a powerful bird, often misjudged by predators with dire results.' WHERE `entry`=9592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I must say, $N, you have learned far more quickly than I first imagined. Looks like we won\'t need to use this last taming totem. And honestly, I\'m not even sure what it is. It appears to be some sort of monstrous lizard with wings and a long tail. Oh well, perhaps another time!$B$BYou\'ve experienced enough to try it on your own now, without the aid of a taming totem. Good luck!' WHERE `entry`=9593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The nightstalker is basically a big kitty with razor sharp claws and an appetite for flesh...' WHERE `entry`=9593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done well in bringing this to me, $N. This is, without a doubt, an armor fragment from a felguard.$B$BThen, it is as I feared. The Nazzivus satyr are renewing their contacts with the Burning Legion. If we don\'t stop them, the satyrs and their demonic allies will overrun us. I will notify Harbinger Mikolaas right away.' WHERE `entry`=9594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='With every spell you must steel yourself against its seductive lure, using it only as needed for the purposes of good. Hopefully the wraith granted a glimpse of what you might turn into should you become careless--a mindless slave to magic.' WHERE `entry`=9595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc8`='<UNUSED>',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you $N! I am glad that Young Furbolg Shaman is fine.$B$BYou truly are blessed with the Light! Therefore, you shall use it to brign back the light in everyone!' WHERE `entry`=9599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ahh... it seems it is time.$B$B<Mehlar nods knowingly.>' WHERE `entry`=9601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you need to go to the Exodar?$B$BThat\'s going to be a long trip, but don\'t worry, I have a way to get you there very quickly.' WHERE `entry`=9603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you\'re headed back to Blood Watch with this package? No problem at all, $C. Just speak with me again and we\'ll get you on your way with those supplies.' WHERE `entry`=9605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='THEY HAVE A PIT LORD?!$B$B<The force commander looks around at the stares of the others and then lowers his voice to a whisper.>$B$BThat seals it. They must be using the blood from this pit lord to create new fel orcs that are somehow not aligned with the Burning Legion. And if they can do this to the brown orcs, they can do it to the green ones too. With all of the new Horde orcs streaming in through the Dark Portal, that\'s not good!$B$BWe must strike at the heart of their military might, and soon!' WHERE `entry`=9607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='THEY HAVE A PIT LORD?!$B$B<Nazgrel notices the glances of the others assembled and lowers his voice to a whisper.>$B$BThat seals it. They must be using the blood from this pit lord to create new fel orcs that are somehow not aligned with the Burning Legion. And if they can do this to the Mag\'har brown orcs, they can do it to us!$B$BWe\'ll have to strike at the heart of their military might, and soon!' WHERE `entry`=9608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you scouted all of the Blood Furnace yet? What do you have to tell me?' WHERE `entry`=9608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='What?  A draenei sent you here from the Harborage?  How odd.$B$BWell, I\'m not one to turn down assistance. Thanks for coming, $C!' WHERE `entry`=9609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Obtain 10 Atal\'ai Artifacts and return them to Holaaru at the Harborage in the Swamp of Sorrows.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='I thank you, $C. The study of these artifacts should keep me occupied for some time. How else are we Broken and draenei to fit in if we do not come to understand the history of your world?' WHERE `entry`=9610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. Well done indeed! You are turning out to be a special $R - a cut above the others of your age. Take this as a reward!' WHERE `entry`=9612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='By the beardless, geometric head of O\'ros! It is good you brought this to me, $N. These blood elves are out for... well, blood. Velen will be informed at once! Take this as a reward.' WHERE `entry`=9616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N, it is good you have come. Our list of allies grows thin, and even those who share our cause are not completely trusted. It is because of this that we, the rangers, turn to nature for aid.$B$BIn the allies of the forest we find a deep bond that does not know deceit.' WHERE `entry`=9617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='All of these reports are from Keltus?  He\'s been quite busy, that\'s for sure.$B$BKeltus is a $C among rogues--he rarely follows orders to the letter, and often takes matters into his own hands!  Don\'t take that wrong, however, as he is one of my most trusted spies and we would be lost without him.$B$BYou\'ve done an exemplary job today. Please accept this blade and guide it into our enemy\'s back.' WHERE `entry`=9618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m impressed you are standing here, $N. Many an apprentice has perished to the voidwalker, or even the voidstone itself.$B$BThe voidwalker is now yours to command. Use your new servant well.' WHERE `entry`=9619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did the device work? Have you marked the murlocs for my research?' WHERE `entry`=9629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Archmage Alturus at Deadwind Pass wants you go into Karazhan and speak to Wravien.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='A vast wealth of information... I could spend years here!  I\'m sure Dalaran will understand...' WHERE `entry`=9630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Alturus wants to raise a whole dragon back from the dead? Not an easy task by any stretch of the imagination.$B$BLet us discuss how we can be of mutual assistance, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Take the Letter of Introduction to Huntress Kella Nightbow.' WHERE `entry`=9632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Alright!  Now if we only had a stretchy loop, a parchment clamp, a guzzle tube and some sticky duck ribbon. Then we could really make something!$B$BOk, ok, I guess you\'ve earned this, $N. Have fun!' WHERE `entry`=9635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Shiny!  And really, what engineer ever has enough spare parts just hanging around?  Ooh, maybe I could sell off the extra and buy me some of that Tigule and Foror\'s Strawberry Ice Cream?!  I just love strawberries!  Do you think they have any around here?$B$BOk, ok, I guess you\'ve earned this, $N. Have fun!' WHERE `entry`=9636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent, $N. I\'ve been trying to attempt these books for a very long time. It is fortunate that we were able to be of mutual assistance.' WHERE `entry`=9637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Can\'t you see I\'m in the middle of something here? What do you want?' WHERE `entry`=9638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The journal you speak of... I was sent here to look for it wasn\'t I?' WHERE `entry`=9639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Did you find what you were looking for? You were looking for something, weren\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=9640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Very well, here are the crystals that I have, $N. Use them well.' WHERE `entry`=9642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='Our preparations are complete. I have put the materials you gathered into this urn. Take it to the Master\'s Terrace, where the fight took place, and set it on fire.$B$BThe energy released will bring life back to the charred remains of Arcanagos. Defeat the creature and retrieve its essence immediately!  You will need to take it to Alturus.$B$BShould you fail, the stars predict you will have let a great terror loose upon the skies.$B$BA terror known as Nightbane!',`objectives_loc8`='Go to the Master\'s Terrace in Karazhan and use Kalynna\'s Urn to summon Nightbane. Retrieve the Faint Arcane Essence from Nightbane\'s corpse and bring it to Archmage Alturus.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is astounding! Not only have you brought back Medivh\'s Journal, but you\'ve also retrieved a fragment of his very essence.$B$BAs faint as this lingering essence is, it will reveal to us vital information about Medivh. We will not forget this, $C.' WHERE `entry`=9644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is a shame that the agents we sent succumbed to Karazhan\'s magic. At least you managed to obtain what they were after.' WHERE `entry`=9645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You\'ve returned! What news do you bring?' WHERE `entry`=9645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='When the towers are under our control, we will soon be able to surround the Forsaken. After that, it is only a matter of time before we can crush them.' WHERE `entry`=9664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is good news, $N. It will be a constant struggle here in the Plaguelands until we have fully driven back the forces of the Alliance.$B$BUntil that day, I hope that we will have your continued assistance.' WHERE `entry`=9665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='They must be fools to think that we would allow them to establish bases so close to one of our capitals.$B$BWe will bleed their numbers until they turn tail and retreat back to the south.' WHERE `entry`=9665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Once again you have proven yourself to be all that was prophesied. You have the eternal gratitude of the high chief $N -- and these Stillpine relics to choose from...' WHERE `entry`=9667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I don\'t have much longer, $N. They will kill me soon...' WHERE `entry`=9667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Are you $N? It\'s about time! I\'d just about given up on finding you!$B$BThere\'s an urgent message waiting for you at the mailbox. The person that gave it to me was a human admiral from Azuremyst. Admiral Odesy-something... the name escapes me. He said you would know who he was.$B$B<Hermesius shrugs.>' WHERE `entry`=9671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Have you heard of the bloodcurse, landlubber? No, of course you haven\'t. The bloodcurse is what sunk all these ships. The spoiled, desecrated part of the water here is known as Bloodcursed Reef - a part of the world you never want to visit. I\'ve been here myself for 20 years.$B$BScurvy my foot! I died on these wild shores as food for the dragons... Ah, but that\'s another story for another time. Right now, we have to help the poor souls that are trapped in that reef.' WHERE `entry`=9672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you\'ve learned a bit, have you?$B$B<Halthenis looks at you carefully.>$B$BYou\'ll serve the city, and our greater cause, well with your newly-learned skills. Allow me a moment to show you how to train your pet to do some interesting tricks, like disemboweling your enemy, and you can be on your way.' WHERE `entry`=9673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Knowing how to feed and revive your pet from death is not just an extra "tidbit" as your last teacher so mildly put it. Even more so, training allows your pet to improve in ways they couldn\'t have on their own.$B$BI\'ve already learned much from the furbolgs, so pay attention and I\'ll pass the knowledge on to you.' WHERE `entry`=9675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome, young initiate. That you have answered my summons so promptly bodes well for you.$B$BLet us dispense with pleasantries, then, as they are best left to courtiers and their ilk.$B$BYour rapid progress has caught my attention, $N. We will see if you have taken your lessons to heart.' WHERE `entry`=9677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I know what must be going through your mind.$B$BYes, I sent Stillblade to kill you.$B$BDo not take offense, $N; it was a necessary test. The Blood Knights are a brotherhood, but we must ensure that our brothers are alert and prepared at all times. Was it necessary to take Stillblade\'s life to make the point to you?$B$BYes, and that is as much a part of your training as any sword drill.' WHERE `entry`=9678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! Though small in size, this fragment is teeming with energy, I can feel it!' WHERE `entry`=9680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome, young $C.$B$BThe power of the Blood Knights is taken from a being of immense power.$B$B<The magister gestures to the large, captive being in the center of the room.>$B$BIsn\'t it magnificent? \'Twas a gift from our beloved Prince Kael\'thas, and it is the foundation of the Blood Knights\' mastery of the Light. This creature begrudges us its power, so we have devised a method for claiming it on our own terms.' WHERE `entry`=9681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have done the hopeless ones a great service, $N. There is but one final task: Destroy the leader of the Bloodcursed.' WHERE `entry`=9682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='Take this vessel, $N. The enchantment it bears will allow you to draw the last vestiges of the Light surrounding these magisters. They once tended the captive naaru and some of its energy yet remains within them.$B$BIt will be just enough to restore your comrade to life.$B$B.Do not worry about the magisters, $N. I have seen to their care, and Lord Solanar assures me that Lady Liadrin seeks a new source of power even now.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. The powers granted by the Light will never come \'naturally\' to the Blood Knights, but we are not so naive as to be thwarted by the will of a single being, however powerful.$B$BOur mastery of the arcane has unlocked this path and these powers for you, initiate. Few have the stomach or the aptitude to wield them, but I know you will not disappoint the order.' WHERE `entry`=9684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome back, initiate. Now that you know the truth about the source of our power and you have demonstrated your skill in wielding it, I will grant you the ability to resurrect the fallen in the field.$B$BStay true to the order and excel at your training and you will only continue to grow in power.' WHERE `entry`=9685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N! You have proven yourself worthy of full membership in the Blood Knights and elevation to adept status. However, there are a few more tasks that remain before your induction can take place.' WHERE `entry`=9686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='A Blood Knight would rather die than submit to the enemy. Remember that, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='When you are ready, I will tell you more about the trial you are to undergo. Make your preparations and speak to me again when you wish to begin.' WHERE `entry`=9690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I knew you had the potential to pass the trial, $N. Your remaining duties are mostly ceremonial, but they are no less dangerous than staring down one of our champions with his weapon drawn. Listen closely, and I will tell you what else you must do to claim your new rank.' WHERE `entry`=9691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent, $N. It\'s all here. All that remains is to forge the weapon.' WHERE `entry`=9692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The outrunner\'s belongings have all been stolen with the exception of one package. It seems to match Alarion\'s description of Erona\'s package.' WHERE `entry`=9704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='By the Sunwell!  That\'s the third outrunner we\'ve lost this month.$B$BI appreciate your courage in venturing into Dawning Street. The guards need to keep a closer eye on these blasted Wretched.' WHERE `entry`=9705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It looks like you\'ve got everything I\'ll need. Let\'s get started!' WHERE `entry`=9707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Here it is, $N. Use it well in the service of Silvermoon and your order.' WHERE `entry`=9710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='Matis will be brought to justice, $N; and I want you to be the one to find him and bring him back to the Triumvirate.$B$BScour the island for this bastard. Should you find him, use this flare gun. When my trackers see the flare, they\'ll come and assist in capturing Matis. Return to me after he\'s been captured.' WHERE `entry`=9711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We can still use more of the sanguine hibiscus from the shamblers, bog giants and underbats of the Underbog at Coilfang Reservoir. Bring them to me in bunches of five and I will be most grateful.' WHERE `entry`=9714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The sporeling makes a sound that is vaguely reminiscent of snorting laughter.>$B$BPerfect! No doubt the morale of the spore giants will be at an all time low once they realize what you\'ve done.$B$BEither that, or they\'ll be so incensed that they\'ll attack us again soon.$B$B<T\'shu makes a shrugging motion.>' WHERE `entry`=9717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We will discuss the purpose for your visit soon. First. let me say that I am indeed impressed by your service and your skill in wielding the Light.' WHERE `entry`=9721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That you have chosen to accept my offer speaks well of you, $N. I wish you luck in the tasks I am about to set for you, but I\'m certain you\'ll prove yourself more than capable.$B$BI will present the tasks in order from easiest to most difficult and we may begin when you are prepared.' WHERE `entry`=9722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent. It appears everything is here.$B$BDon\'t worry. your next task will include plenty of opportunities to wield your weapon again, I promise.$B$BI\'ll have an initiate bring it all to Magister Astalor. There\'s no need to send you on such a trivial errand when there are more important things to be done.' WHERE `entry`=9723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have done well in demonstrating your loyalty to your homeland and dedication to the needs of the order, $N. I have one last task for you before you may lay claim to the title of master.' WHERE `entry`=9725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Welcome back, $N. Have you beaten back the Scourge and their meatwagons?' WHERE `entry`=9725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Fhwoor\'s a good giant. We saved him from the naga a while ago and he\'s stayed here helping us with things ever since.$B$BWe can only hope that the naga will take the hint and realize that if we can infiltrate their village and steal their most prized possession, we can do much worse. Perhaps now they will return to their reservoir and leave us in peace?' WHERE `entry`=9729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Is Fwhoor alright? Have you recovered the ark?' WHERE `entry`=9729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Search Serpent Lake for signs of a drain. Return to Ysiel Windsinger at Cenarion Refuge with news of your discovery.' WHERE `entry`=9731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hmm... this is a rather small amount. but if we\'re careful. it should be sufficient. You see. the Scarlet Crusade believes itself dedicated to the Light. I suppose they still are, in a twisted sort of way, and that\'s exactly what I\'m hoping to capitalize on.$B$BTheir misguided zeal has even tainted the blessing spoken over this water, making it ideal for my purpose.' WHERE `entry`=9735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Now that we have all the reagents, I can prepare the mixture.$B$B<A slow smile spreads across Lady Liadrin\'s face.>$B$BIt\'s all coming together perfectly, $N. When this is finished, I\'ll give you the details about what remains to be done.' WHERE `entry`=9736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. All who would oppose us would do well to heed the warning you delivered. Our foes should know that they are in peril, from the lowest foot soldier to the mightiest $Ghero:heroine;.$B$BYou have earned your place in the ranks of the masters. Your dedication and prowess serve as an example for all Blood Knights. As a symbol of your new status, I grant you the ability to summon and command the thalassian charger.' WHERE `entry`=9737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you done as I asked and delivered my message? The false paladins of the world must surely know their time has come to an end.' WHERE `entry`=9737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m glad that some of my friends yet live, but it breaks my heart to hear of the fate of others. <sigh>$B$BAt least they died doing what they loved most in life. You have my eternal gratitude for helping me with this, $N.$B$BPlease, take one of these as a sign of gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=9738;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes! You\'ve saved more spore sacs.$B$BYou\'re different than the other outsiders. I\'ll let my people know about your deeds!$B$B<This quest is repeatable up to friendly reputation.>' WHERE `entry`=9742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Unbelievable!  It would take hundreds of sporelings to slay as many giants as you have. I will make sure to let everyone know of your feats!$B$B<This quest is repeatable up to friendly reputation.>' WHERE `entry`=9744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This will surely soften up their defenses and make them think twice before rushing foolishly into our ranks!' WHERE `entry`=9746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Have you heard of the bloodcurse, landlubber? No, of course you haven\'t. The bloodcurse is what sunk all these ships. The spoiled, desecrated part of the water here is known as Bloodcursed Reef - a part of the world you never want to visit. I\'ve been here myself for 20 years.$B$BScurvy my foot! I died on these wild shores as food for the dragons... Ah, but that\'s another story for another time. Right now, we have to help the poor souls that are trapped in that reef.' WHERE `entry`=9751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='A-ha! Well done, $N. Well done, indeed. Are you ready to eradicate the blood elf menace from our island forever?' WHERE `entry`=9756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let\'s begin our lesson at once!' WHERE `entry`=9757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Perhaps you will be the one to deliver our people into a new age of prosperity and peace.' WHERE `entry`=9760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Our biggest enemy in the region is finally dead. You\'ve done the expedition a great favor, $N.$B$BWe shall be forever in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=9763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Vashj!$B$BThis is much more than we bargained for. Our small victories here and there against the naga mean nothing.$B$BIf Lady Vashj is involved in this, then forces much greater than us are at work.$B$BYou\'ve done well in bringing this to us, $N. Now, we must prepare for war.' WHERE `entry`=9764;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These will do perfectly, $N. Bring any more armaments you find. Our need is great and our resources are scarce.' WHERE `entry`=9765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent work, $N. The naga will learn not to underestimate us.' WHERE `entry`=9766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These be fine ones, $N. Here\'s your payment.$B$B<Magasha bends one of the wings and holds it up to her head.>$B$BNope, not my thing, but who\'m I to complain?$B$B<Magasha shrugs.>$B$BCoin speaks.' WHERE `entry`=9769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Had your fill already?$B$B<Reavij laughs.>$B$BThere\'s a reason why our visitors don\'t stay long.$B$BIf I had a choice, I\'d find a more agreeable spot for the post, but I\'ll take marshfangs over Denjai\'s temper any day.' WHERE `entry`=9770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Search for Scout Jyoba.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='The battered corpse matches Zurai\'s description perfectly. Whatever killed the scout appears to have taken him by surprise, as his weapon is sheathed and the contents of a small inkwell stain the nearby ground.' WHERE `entry`=9771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Zurai accepts the report from you and glances over it.>$B$BMuch of this is information we already know. Everything in the area seems to be dried or wilting, but here\'s something new.$B$BHe says the fungal giants seem to have gone berserk from the lack of moisture. From your description, that must be what killed him.$B$BI\'ll instruct my men to avoid the area. We can\'t afford any more casualties.' WHERE `entry`=9772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Finally, a break from the monotony of mushrooms! If you didn\'t smell like fish, I\'d hug you.$B$BLet\'s see how jealous the others get when they smell the meat cooking over the fire.' WHERE `entry`=9773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $N. Every little bit helps.$B$BI\'ve still got a long way to go, but let\'s face it, what else am I going to do between patrols?' WHERE `entry`=9774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Bring Zurai\'s Report to Shadow Hunter Denjai in Zabra\'jin',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Why didn\'t you say you had a report from Zurai? I\'ve been waiting to hear from him.$B$BI sent him out there to give us a presence on the eastern border, not sit on his hands. Let\'s see what he has to say.' WHERE `entry`=9775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Speak to Ikuti at the Orebor Harborage.' WHERE `entry`=9776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ysiel sent you? Of course I can use someone like you! We\'re always in need of a little muscle.' WHERE `entry`=9778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you for your help, $N. Your generosity will not be forgotten. As a token of my gratitude, I\'ve prepared a hot drink for you.' WHERE `entry`=9780;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent. Keep bringing me more plant parts if you find any.$B$B<This quest is repeatable up to Honored reputation.>' WHERE `entry`=9784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Hunt down 30 Clefthoof and return to Hemet Nesingwary at Nesingwary\'s Safari in Nagrand to prove yourself.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='A fair start. But that\'s just the beginning.$B$BThe lesser clefthoof prove nothing. Let\'s move you up to a bigger challenge' WHERE `entry`=9789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m flattered that your Broken friend considers me a scholar of his people\'s relics, but to be honest, I haven\'t had much chance to study them since my arrival here. It was certainly my intent, but when I arrived, I found that there were other matters that required my attention.' WHERE `entry`=9792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you\'ve brought Timothy\'s response?$B$B<Kialon pauses a moment to read the letter, then laughs.>$B$BHe\'s got everything under control, he says. Doesn\'t need help, he says. I could\'ve predicted that!$B$BSome people never change. Look, he even took the time to correct my spelling.$B$B<Kialon lets out a half-hearted sigh.>$B$BI shouldn\'t have sent the letter. I forgot. The specialist always has the situation under control. Always.' WHERE `entry`=9794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s about time he got that outpost up and running. We\'ve lost far too many runners to Alliance outriders.' WHERE `entry`=9796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These look like fine specimens. Thank you for performing the field work. Once I can find the time to analyze these, I should be able to tell what it will take to restore the fields.' WHERE `entry`=9799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Elementalist Lo\'ap at the Throne of the Elements in Nagrand wants you to bring him 15 Digested Caracoli.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Please do not wash yourself in the sacred waters of the Throne.$B$B<Elementalist Lo\'ap holds a prepared caracoli tablet up.>$B$BYou place this under your tongue and allow it ample time to dissolve. Once it has dissolved, you will be able to breathe water as if it were air.' WHERE `entry`=9800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Anchorite Ahuurn at Telredor wants you to bring him 4 Spore Bat Eyes and 4 Fen Strider Tentacles.' WHERE `entry`=9801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Elementalist Lo\'ap at the Throne of the Elements in Nagrand wants you to destroy 12 Lake Spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Elementalist Lo\'ap kneels in the water and says a prayer.>$B$BThe Earthen Ring takes no pride in what was done. We do what we must to heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=9804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your efforts have stifled the spread of pollution but other troubles have surfaced.' WHERE `entry`=9805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='With great shame I tell you that it is my own kin who seek to drudge up the waters of Nagrand and create marshland.' WHERE `entry`=9805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your help is appreciated, $N. You will keep it up, yes?' WHERE `entry`=9807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This will help us trade with other sporelings for food and supplies. Sporeggar thanks you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=9808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $N. As Sporeggar\'s elder, I must ensure my people have adequate supplies. You make my task that much easier.' WHERE `entry`=9809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Elementalist Lo\'ap at the Throne of the Elements in Nagrand wants you to destroy Watoosun\'s Polluted Essence and 10 Lake Surgers.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='The elements sang of your victory the moment the disturbed essence was destroyed! The Earthen Ring thanks you and wishes for you to choose a reward.' WHERE `entry`=9810;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you killed Dar\'Khan, $R?  Impressive. I\'ve a feeling my people and yours will soon get to be very good friends.' WHERE `entry`=9811;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is done then. The foul traitor got what he deserved.$B$BYou\'ve been of great service to the blood elves and to the Horde. Dar\'khan was Thrall\'s excuse to deny them entry into our alliance. You\'ve cleared the way for a new Horde, $C.$B$BI also see that Lor\'themar has additional news that will greatly improve his relations with Thrall. Excellent!' WHERE `entry`=9812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Thrall begins to read the letter.>So the blood elves finally took care of their little problem. Never mind that it took your help as well as that of an entire Forsaken regiment to get the job done.<Thrall breaks into laughter.>I suppose there\'s no stopping this. In the end we need them just as much as they need us. Welcome to the horde Blood Elf.' WHERE `entry`=9813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These be excellent, mon!$B$BI\'ll tell you what. Since you been a good sport and helped with the mushrooms, I\'ll let you in on the fun!' WHERE `entry`=9814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Earthen Ring thanks you, $N. The elements also give their thanks. Your continued efforts in cleansing our world are appreciated and noted.' WHERE `entry`=9815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent work, mon! I do hope they had a good time!' WHERE `entry`=9816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='<Witch Doctor Tor\'gash grins.>$B$BDid the lil\' Lost Ones like their gift?' WHERE `entry`=9816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Gordawg appears to be nodding at you.>$B$BSit.' WHERE `entry`=9818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Gordawg at the Throne of the Elements in Nagrand has asked that you destroy 15 Tortured Earth Spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Gordawg nods in approval.>$B$BGood. Spirits sleep now.' WHERE `entry`=9819;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. The presence of these ogres so close to our outpost does have me worried, though. It seems like they\'ve been filtering down from the northern mountains for some time.' WHERE `entry`=9820;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Gordawg at the Throne of the Elements in Nagrand has asked that you bring him 15 Enraged Crusher Cores.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Gordawg spits out the chewed up rock, pelting you with a hail of rubble.>$B$BPoison. These rocks are not Nagrand. These rocks are from poison. You destroy poison rock. You find usurper.' WHERE `entry`=9821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Shadow Hunter Denjai examines the plans.>$B$BI knew it! The stench of ogres always carries an implicit threat. Now that we have proof of their intentions, we must act before they do.' WHERE `entry`=9822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your victory over the Ango\'rosh is to be celebrated, $N. I wonder how long it will be before those ogre brutes find themselves another bloodthirsty chieftain.$B$BNo matter, we\'ll be ready for them.' WHERE `entry`=9823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These readings do not bode well, $N. Karazhan should be emanating all manner of arcane currents... instead it has become a huge energy vacuum. No signals. Nothing. Except for a very faint demonic echo.$B$BThis is bad news, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The readings, $N. Did you complete them?' WHERE `entry`=9824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Fascinating. I will study these essences, $N. I thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=9825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='These signs do not bode well for us, $N. I\'ve never been one for secrecy so I will tell you a bit about my organization, the Violet Eye.$B$BWe are agents of the Kirin Tor, the Magus Senate of Dalaran. We were assigned to keep an eye on Karazhan and Medivh, in case things got out of hand.$B$BWhich they did... very quickly, after Medivh disappeared.$B$BThis report details my findings. Take it to Archmage Cedric, also from the Violet Eye; you will find him in the outskirts of Dalaran.',`objectives_loc8`='Bring Alturus\'s Report to Archmage Cedric in the outskirts of Dalaran.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You know of the Violet Eye? You do not look familiar.' WHERE `entry`=9826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Take the Withered Basidium to Ruam in Telredor.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='It looks like the basidium of a bog giant. but I haven\'t seen one in this condition before. I\'d heard that the giants in the Dead Mire had begun to wither. but it\'s far more advanced than I expected.$B$BThe Dead Mire was once a lake like the others in the marsh, and it served as the spawning ground for the giants. With the waters receding, it seems the changes are preventing the giants from sporing. If this continues, the giants may disappear entirely.' WHERE `entry`=9827;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Bring the Withered Basidium to Reavij at Swamprat Post.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='It looks like the basidium of a boglord, but I haven\'t seen one in this condition before. I\'d heard that the giants in the Dead Mire had begun to wither, but it\'s far more advanced than I expected.$B$BThe Dead Mire was once a lake like the others in the marsh, and it served as the spawning ground for the giants. With the waters receding, it seems the changes are preventing the giants from sporing. If this continues, the giants may disappear entirely.' WHERE `entry`=9828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Violet Eye? You don\'t say.$B$BShow me this report you speak of.' WHERE `entry`=9829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done well, $N. I wasn\'t sure you would succeed.$B$BThe containers are enchanted with a potent spell that masks their presence from unworthy eyes. I\'m glad to see they did not elude you.' WHERE `entry`=9831;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have the fragments. This is most impressive, $N. You\'re certainly worthy of holding the key to Karazhan.$B A small problem remains.' WHERE `entry`=9832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That key, I recognize it. That is Kadghar\'s key... of course I haven\'t given it to him yet.' WHERE `entry`=9836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Who are you and what do you want?' WHERE `entry`=9836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='His own key? That\'s incredible!$B$BI do not sense any disturbances in our timeline, so I suppose it was meant to occur all along. There\'s no turning back now, $N. The key is yours and only yours.' WHERE `entry`=9837;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I sent you to deliver a report and you come back with a key to this place? There must be more to you than meets the eye, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Koren looks at you with an uncertain look.>$B$BI know nothing of this Violet Eye you speak of. A blacksmith is all I am.' WHERE `entry`=9840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I thought so. I can hear the difference already. I\'ll finally be able to get back to work, thanks to you. If you ever find yourself in need of tradeskill supplies, don\'t forget ol\' Gambarinka!' WHERE `entry`=9841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These should keep me supplied for some time to come! I think some of the others have begun to take notice. I\'ve had several offers to buy my blades already. Selling them on the side might provide better business than my customary goods.' WHERE `entry`=9842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You found the log. I sure hope the information we need is in here, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You did it! Yes, the readings are becoming normal once again!$B$BWe must give this news to Cedric. He\'s going to be very impressed with your achievement.' WHERE `entry`=9844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I dread to ask, $N. What has become of the situation inside Karazhan?' WHERE `entry`=9844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I can\'t wait to return to fishing! Now I\'ll be able to return to town with some real fish in my bucket and Gambarinka won\'t be able to make fun of me anymore!' WHERE `entry`=9845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hmm... They seem to be divided between images of a serpent spirit and a bird spirit. No self-respecting Darkspear troll engages in bird worship. Their spirits are weak, capricious, and best left to the Amani.$B$BBut the serpent, $N, the serpent wields considerable power and this is the spirit I shall study.' WHERE `entry`=9846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You tell Seer Janidi about what happened when you used the totem.>$B$BThe spirit attacked you? It must have a higher affinity for those Lost Ones than I\'d thought. There\'s no way to compel it to serve me without expending considerable effort. I\'ll have to search for a new source of power in this wretched world.' WHERE `entry`=9847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Were you able to summon the Feralfen spirit?' WHERE `entry`=9847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='GUROK! Gurok betrayed the elements!' WHERE `entry`=9849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='You\'ve proved to me that you can find and take down a regular clefthoof, but far more dangerous are the clefthoof bulls.$B$BBag yourself thirty of those. Then you can talk to me of your hunting prowess.$B$BLook for them all along the middle region of Nagrand to the west and south.',`objectives_loc8`='Kill 30 Clefthoof Bulls and then speak to Hemet Nesingwary at Nesingwary\'s Safari in Nagrand about your prowess.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Impressive. Most impressive.$B$BYou\'ve got potential, kid. Now I\'m going to give you the chance to have some real fun!' WHERE `entry`=9850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You did it! You took down Banthar! I never had a doubt, $N.$B$BHere, I think you\'ve more than earned this.' WHERE `entry`=9851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Gordawg chomps down hard on Gurok\'s earthen head, nearly disintegrating the stone formation.>$B$BGurok\'s reign has come to an end. The earthen elements are free. All sleep now. Champion gets reward!' WHERE `entry`=9853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill 30 Windrocs and then return to Fitz at the Nesingwary Safari in Nagrand.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Every day is a gift. Make the most of it. For tomorrow we shall stride swifter over the plains than today. We will spread our arms further and strain to achieve that which tonight we can only dream of, though it may ever elude us.' WHERE `entry`=9854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Hunt down 30 Ravenous Windrocs and then return to Fitz at the Nesingwary Safari in Nagrand.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have proven your skill once more, $C. Now you must go on to stalk the fiercest of the windrocs.' WHERE `entry`=9855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Her eye looks as if it is still alive. Do you think that she can still see into your soul?$B$B$N, you can now count yourself as one of the elite safari hunters. And you are another step closer to stalking the ultimate prey of this land, Tusker!$B$BYou\'ve earned the right to have this. May it serve you well.' WHERE `entry`=9856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill 30 Talbuk Stags and then return to Harold Lane at the Nesingwary Safari in Nagrand.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='That\'s a good tale... <cough>...of how you bagged all of those stags, $C. But I think that you can do better. I\'ve got something else in mind for you.' WHERE `entry`=9857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Hunt down 30 Talbuk Thorngrazers and then return to Harold Lane at the Nesingwary Safari in Nagrand.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<cough>, <cough>... $N! You did it. There\'s only...<cough>... one thing left to...<cough>... do then.' WHERE `entry`=9858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Wow! You did it! That\'s really Bach\'lor\'s hoof!$B$BUm, I\'m starting to feel much better it would seem. Here, let me give you something in celebration of your proven hunting prowess!' WHERE `entry`=9859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Speak to Archmage Cedric in the Outskirts of Dalaran.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Alturus told me all about what happened, $N. This is not the end of it, however. With Karazhan remaining sealed to outsiders, it\'s only a matter of time until the Legion renews its attacks while we stand powerless in the sidelines.$B$BUnless you accept the responsibility that fate has bestowed upon you, that is.$B$B<Cedric extends an open palm towards you, holding a badge with the Violet Eye\'s symbol on it.>$B$BWhat do you say, $N?' WHERE `entry`=9860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Elementalist Morgh at the Throne of the Elements in Nagrand wants you to slay 8 Murkblood Putrifiers.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You saw them controlling the elements? The wind bent to their will?$B$B<Morgh is lost in thought for a moment.>$B$BThis is troubling, $N. I must consult with the others.$B$BWe thank you for your efforts, $N. Perhaps you should return to your village and see if they have any other information about the Murkbloods and their nefarious goals.' WHERE `entry`=9862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Farseer Kurkush at Garadar in Nagrand wants you to bring him 20 Murkblood Idols.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have given the Lightning Sons hope, $N. If our leader will not protect us, perhaps there are others that are capable - like you.' WHERE `entry`=9863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I have been told stories of my people. They say that once, we were warriors...' WHERE `entry`=9864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill 40 Murkblood Scavengers and 20 Murkblood Raiders.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Saurfang turns to face you.>$B$BIs it blood that I smell? I regret being unable to lend assistance. How proud you must be. My chest swells just knowing what you have done.$B$BAre there others like you? Where you come from, do more heroes exist?' WHERE `entry`=9865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Farseer Corhuk stares at the ground, lost in contemplation. He nods his head affirmatively.>$B$B<Farseer Corhuk wipes a tear away.>$B$BThe son is the father... May the spirits have mercy on those that stand in his way.' WHERE `entry`=9866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So, this is the face of our enemy? I will have this put upon a pike and placed outside of Garadar, near the gates. Should they think to attack us again, they will see the consequences for their actions looking down upon them...' WHERE `entry`=9867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='What does it matter? The Greatmother is dying. Life is not worth living...' WHERE `entry`=9868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='<Garrosh barely acknowledges your presence. He appears deeply depressed.>' WHERE `entry`=9868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, thank you for the message. Perhaps you would not mind helping out the Earthen Ring? The elements are in flux. We can use all of the assistance that we can get.' WHERE `entry`=9869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, thank you for the message. Perhaps you would not mind helping out the Earthen Ring? The elements are in flux. We can use all of the assistance that we can get.' WHERE `entry`=9870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Take the Murkblood Invasion Plans to Arechron.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Arechron slams his fist into his hand.>Ortor... Treacherous bastard!' WHERE `entry`=9871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='A thousand dead orcs you say? What could have triggered such an audacious advance into orc lands? It is good that he is dead but there is more to this than what meets the tentacle.' WHERE `entry`=9873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Otonbu sighs.>$B$BThis will set back any chance of peace with the orcs another 10 years. At least we will be around to see those years as opposed to what could have happened had those corpses been allowed to rot.' WHERE `entry`=9874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The orcs will not understand what we are doing but it must be done. For the good of both orc and Broken.' WHERE `entry`=9874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='A new species! Are you sure?$B$B<Lauranna flips through pages of notes and diagrams.>$B$BNice job, $N. We\'ll have to add this one to our list. How does "Purple Leafed $Nrium" sound to you?  It does have a ring to it.' WHERE `entry`=9875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Ysiel Windsinger wants you to look for signs of Cenarion Expedition Druids near the entrance to Coilfang Reservoir.' WHERE `entry`=9876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Poli\'lukluk the Wiser at Telaar in Nagrand wants you to kill 20 Murkblood Scavengers and 10 Murkblood Raiders.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is doubtful that the orcs will understand or appreciate what you just did but Nagrand is better off for the deed. Thank you, problem solver...' WHERE `entry`=9878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes, I know of the totem... but there is much more to this story. Alas, I lack the authority to reveal this information to you. Only the chosen may be privy to such knowledge.' WHERE `entry`=9879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Color me impressed. These are in excellent condition, for the most part.$B$BI will make sure to put in a good word for you with our people.' WHERE `entry`=9882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Keep the crystal fragments coming, $N. We cannot let these thieves take our property.$B$BEven if it\'s not ours just quite yet. A technicality, of course.' WHERE `entry`=9883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Consortium is well known for taking good care of its friends. At the beginning of each month I\'ll have some gems ready for you as payment for your services.$B$BThe quality of the gems you get will depend on how loyal you\'ve been to us. Here\'s to hoping you do the smart thing and stay with us.' WHERE `entry`=9884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Consortium is well known for taking good care of its friends. At the beginning of each month I\'ll have some gems ready for you as payment for your services.$B$BThe quality of the gems you get will depend on how loyal you\'ve been to us. Here\'s to hoping you do the smart thing and stay with us.' WHERE `entry`=9885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Consortium is well known for taking good care of its friends. At the beginning of each month I\'ll have some gems ready for you as payment for your services.$B$BThe quality of the gems you get will depend on how loyal you\'ve been to us. Here\'s to hoping you do the smart thing and stay with us.' WHERE `entry`=9886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Consortium is well known for taking good care of its friends. At the beginning of each month I\'ll have some gems ready for you as payment for your services.$B$BThe quality of the gems you get will depend on how loyal you\'ve been to us. Here\'s to hoping you do the smart thing and stay with us.' WHERE `entry`=9887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I submit! I submit!' WHERE `entry`=9889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We\'ll make a good profit on these, $N. I\'ll make sure Khoraazi hears about your work here.' WHERE `entry`=9892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent. This will keep us in business while we wait for the Sha\'tar to finish whatever housekeeping it is they need to do inside Oshu\'gun.' WHERE `entry`=9893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I can\'t thank you enough. I\'m going to enjoy this...' WHERE `entry`=9896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well, I couldn\'t see if you helped out with saving Kristen, or not. But if she handed you one of her bundles of skins then you\'re alright in my book.Here\'s your reward.' WHERE `entry`=9897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Fantastic! I\'ll never forget how you helped me to win her heart. In fact, you can be a guest of honor at our wedding.' WHERE `entry`=9898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='At least someone is pulling $G his:her; weight around here. Thank you for taking care of that matter, $N. I need to have a word with Zurai about Reavij. His scheming and daydreaming have gone on long enough.' WHERE `entry`=9899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We won\'t have to worry about Gava\'xi anymore, thanks to you. Let us arrange for your reward now.' WHERE `entry`=9900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m sure the old boy must\'ve seen his days coming to an end. With all these new arrivals, the old order couldn\'t stand. It\'s just as well his spirit is at rest now.' WHERE `entry`=9903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='At last! They say every great fisherman has a story of "the one that got away," but I haven\'t yet met a creature I couldn\'t beat one way or another.' WHERE `entry`=9904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Jorin Deadeye at Garadar in Nagrand has asked that you slay 15 Boulderfist Crushers and 15 Boulderfist Mystics.' WHERE `entry`=9906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Jorin Deadeye at Garadar in Nagrand has asked that you slay 25 Boulderfist Warriors and 25 Boulderfist Mages.' WHERE `entry`=9907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Respect from fear! It is as good as any other kind.' WHERE `entry`=9910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Bring "Count" Ungula\'s Mandible to Watcher Leesa\'oh.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Are you sure that\'s real? I mean, I knew there was large wildlife in the marsh, but there are giant creatures and then there are GIANT bugs.$B$BCome to think of it, the sporelings did mention a story about a fearsome nether ray that used to terrorize them before the boglord incursion.$B$BWhat if the stories are true? Oh, dear. I\'d better take that for safekeeping. The expedition will want to know about this.' WHERE `entry`=9911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Are you ready to get to work, $R? I think I\'ve got the perfect task for you.' WHERE `entry`=9913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Never doubted you for a second, friend. Most of those look like fine specimens, if a bit dirty and scratched up. Still, I think they\'re worth the value we agreed upon previously.$B$BI hope that we can continue to do business in the future.' WHERE `entry`=9914;
