UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Chief Researcher Amereldine at Halaa wants 20 Oshu\'gun Crystal Powder Samples.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Wonderful, $N. This will help us in our battle against the Alliance filth that have surfaced in the Outland.' WHERE `entry`=10074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am always accepting crystal powder contributions, $N. You will be compensated for each set of samples that you recover.' WHERE `entry`=10075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Chief Researcher Kartos at Halaa wants 20 Oshu\'gun Crystal Powder Samples.' WHERE `entry`=10076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I thank you for your contribution, $N. Should you find more, you know where to bring them!' WHERE `entry`=10077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The potion that you drank has no real effect. You can only see a spirit if they allow it. The potion is merely a symbol of your belief and dedication. It was a test and you passed...' WHERE `entry`=10081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Mother Kashur has asked that you put to rest 15 Agitated Orc Spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s no use. They continue to rise. There must be something more insidious underway.' WHERE `entry`=10082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is very troubling. You say that none of the ancestors were at their villages? That they were all moving south?' WHERE `entry`=10085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Move as the wind, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='At last! Now, I don\'t suppose you\'re willing to bop a few peons on the head, or will that cost extra?' WHERE `entry`=10088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='To\'gun was here earlier giving me his report. He should have stayed with you to help!$B$BI sent him back out there to assist Grik\'tha. I think they make a cute couple.$B$BSo, these are the soul devices that the Shadow Council were using to enhance their summoning power? They look dangerous to me' WHERE `entry`=10091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Opening the magically suspended tome, a sense of dread overwhelms you.$B$BSomething is most definitely wrong here!$B$BYou read on, but what you read seems unbelievable!' WHERE `entry`=10094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Murmur almost broke free?! They\'ve had that thing contained in there for two years... I wonder what they did wrong to lose control over it after all this time?$B$B$N, by putting that beast down you\'ve likely saved all of us! I cringe to think what would have happened to all of us here, and the rest of Outland, if that thing had somehow managed to break free!$B$BI\'m glad you helped us to take matters into our own hands and deal with the Shadow Council threat at Auchindoun. How can we ever reward you?' WHERE `entry`=10095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I can\'t thank you enough, $N. Knowing that Lakka is free means I can cut the rest of my ties to the Sethekk.$B$BPart of me will never forgive myself for Syth\'s death, but it had to be done. When I reach Skettis, I will perform the death rites for him. Perhaps his spirit will find rest once it has atoned for leading our people astray.' WHERE `entry`=10097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did you find her, $N? Was she still being held within the halls?' WHERE `entry`=10097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I may never truly be forgiven for my role in the crimes of the Sethekk, but perhaps by restoring the relics of Terokk to my people, I can begin to redeem myself.$B$BThank you for helping me in this, $N. You have no idea of the magnitude of what you\'ve done this day.' WHERE `entry`=10098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hopefully, getting rid of their overseer will cause the leftovers to panic and break. Should be easy cleanup for my boys, once I\'ve found a way to keep them awake, that is.' WHERE `entry`=10100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<A gentle, melodic voice fills your mind.>$B$BI am K\'ure of the naaru, $N. You stand within the heart of my ancient vessel.$B$BOshu\'gun, as the orcs named it, is the ship that first brought the draenei to this world. Though we fell from the heavens and crashed here many hundreds of years ago, my weakened energies have remained trapped within this wreckage. Regrettably, I am the source of the orc spirits\' pain.' WHERE `entry`=10101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='K\'ure was wise to send you here. While we cannot assist you with the suffering of the orc ancestors, there is one that can.$B$BOne that is soon to be reborn of Light...' WHERE `entry`=10102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m flattered that your Broken friend considers me a scholar of his people\'s relics, but to be honest, I haven\'t had much chance to study them since my arrival here. It was certainly my intent, but when I arrived, I found that there were other matters that required my attention.' WHERE `entry`=10104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='Now that Swamprat Post is complete, our control of the roads in and out of the marsh is much less tenuous. Our presence in Terokkar Forest is much less secure. Even so, at Stonebreaker Hold, Rakoria awaits word of our progress.$B$BShe\'s sharp and capable, $N, but be careful around her. She\'s got a lot of a goods she\'s eager to move along the roads, but don\'t assume she\'s got our best interests at heart. Rakoria goes where she believes there\'s profit to be found.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'d hoped his men would have the outpost complete sooner, but it\'s not costing him money. Still, it\'s progress.' WHERE `entry`=10105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='$N, return to me when you have aided in the capture of each of the forts!' WHERE `entry`=10106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So what is your decision? Will it be war or will you lend your assistance?' WHERE `entry`=10107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So what is your decision? Will it be war or will you lend your assistance?' WHERE `entry`=10108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! Now just a few adjustments and this thing will be as good as new. Oh yes, your key! Here you go.$B$BBy the way, the Jump-a-tron still has a few kinks that I need to work out. Um, just be careful.' WHERE `entry`=10109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well, it\'s no egg... Hey! I love chicken too! I\'ll just chomp right through this ginourmous talon! Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=10111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did I mention my love for eggs? Completion' WHERE `entry`=10111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes, indeed, I do believe that it\'s all getting clearer now.$B$BAnd I think that your diligence in this matter deserves more than just the information that you seek.' WHERE `entry`=10112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I suppose we\'ll have to find a replacement water boy. Say, you look like a powerful $C. Interested in a job? Or did you come for the hunt?' WHERE `entry`=10113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am relieved to hear that he is safe. Have you come to join the hunt?' WHERE `entry`=10114;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have my thanks, $N. I was beginning to think that I was going to have to take a substantial part of the garrison up there and deal with Mummaki myself. Of course, there\'s no telling what might have happened to Zabra\'jin then.' WHERE `entry`=10117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I think you\'ve managed to send a fairly strong message to them. Perhaps now, the rest of my men won\'t be so afraid to take the fight to the Daggerfen. Or, if they are, they\'ll find themselves ashamed by their lack of bravery.' WHERE `entry`=10118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I wish I could be there to watch the fire display. Those explosives pack a big punch!' WHERE `entry`=10144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done it, $N! The spirits are freed!$B$BAlthough I am without a material manifestation, I am still able to reward you with items from the spirit world. Use them with caution as such items are often volatile and can cause great harm to their user.' WHERE `entry`=10164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Another competitor goes under... You do good work for a flesh beast, $R. If you are ever in Netherstorm, look me up. I make my home at the Stormspire.' WHERE `entry`=10165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The memory is vivid, $N. My energies were wholly drained from the crash. I was only a dim speck of void energies when the Prophet Velen and his draenei compatriots lifted my remains and brought them here. After much ceremony, my diminished form was laid to rest within this sarcophagus. I have been regenerating for nearly a thousand years. The cycle is almost complete...' WHERE `entry`=10167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have completed a long and dangerous journey, risking life and limb to ensure the safety of the Mag\'har and the serenity of our ancestors. For this I am thankful beyond what words could convey.' WHERE `entry`=10168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Aldor marksmen appear distracted with their drill, allowing you ample time to place the contents of the vial into the stew.' WHERE `entry`=10169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I want you to personally deliver this news to Garrosh.' WHERE `entry`=10170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Everyone is proud. Proud that our people will live to see another winter. But beyond that? What is there?$B$BMaybe you should lead this clan, $N. Maybe then I will be allowed to die when the Greatmother passes. Allowed to finally erase the shame of my family name. I long for such peace.' WHERE `entry`=10171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Tears stream down Greatmother Geyah\'s face.>$B$BSeek out your warchief. Tell him that I await him here...' WHERE `entry`=10172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='<Greatmother Geyah is lying down.>' WHERE `entry`=10172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, so you managed to recover the staff. Impressive, $N. Perhaps you are the one I\'ve been looking for.$B$BOh yes, your reward...$B$B<Ravandwyr presses a few coins into your palm.>$B$BNo doubt you had higher expectations, but that too will come with time. For now, consider opportunity the true reward.' WHERE `entry`=10173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Thrall\'s voice takes on the hollow essence of a storm cloud.>I... I have a grandmother? She lives?' WHERE `entry`=10175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='What? Grik\'tha sent you in here after me?$B$BI don\'t know whether to be touched or call her a fool!$B$BDo you think you could help me get out of this cage? It\'s a bit cramped.' WHERE `entry`=10178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What have you found, $N?' WHERE `entry`=10182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, Coppernickels finally decided to report his findings, did he?  Lazy scientists!$B$BWhat\'s this?$B$B<The chief riffles through the notations a few times, clearly with a look of disbelief.>$B$BHe says here that the violent nether-energies flowing through the Netherstorm are going to rip everything to shreds in only a few months.$B$BThat\'s inconvenient - now we\'ll have to move up the time-table on building the rocket ship!' WHERE `entry`=10183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The custodian looks dismayed.>$B$BI can already see the next wave coming over the horizon. Culling them will work for the time being, but more permanent measures are needed.' WHERE `entry`=10185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Retrieve the Sigil of Krasus from Spellbinder Maryana at Manaforge Coruu, northwest of the Violet Tower. When you have gained the sigil, use Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff to project an Image of Archmage Vargoth and inform him of your progress.$B$BIf you lose Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff, speak to Ravandwyr at Area 52 to receive a replacement.' WHERE `entry`=10188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! With this roster we can make more educated decisions when targeting Kael\'s followers at the manaforges.$B$BIt\'s too bad, I was beginning to take a liking to killing his lackeys indiscriminately.' WHERE `entry`=10189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Back so soon?$B$BIs everything okay with the Maxx A. Million Mk. V?!' WHERE `entry`=10191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Reclaim Krasus\'s Compendium - Chapter 1, Krasus\'s Compendium - Chapter 2, and Krasus\'s Compendium - Chapter 3 from Kirin\'Var Village\'s Town Square. Use Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff to contact the archmage once you have the chapters.$B$BIf you lose Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff, speak to Ravandwyr at Area 52 to receive a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Archmage Vargoth\'s image seems to inspect the compendium.>$B$BIt\'s a little worse for the wear, but considering the treatment it\'s been through, it\'s a miracle all of it survived. Safeguard it, $N. Without it, we stand little chance of being able to break the tower\'s ward.' WHERE `entry`=10192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'re one reliable fellow, $N. If there\'s one thing I like more than killing Kael\'s lapdogs, it is having someone else do it for me.$B$BLess blood on my clothes that way.' WHERE `entry`=10193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Arranging for your flight wasn\'t cheap. Let\'s hope you have what it takes to get the job done.' WHERE `entry`=10194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! When I\'m through with you, you will be able to slip among the Sunfury ranks unnoticed.' WHERE `entry`=10197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use the Sunfury Disguise, go into Manaforge Coruu and listen to the conversation between Commander Dawnforge and Arcanist Ardonis. Report back to Caledis Brightdawn after completing this task.$B$BCompleting tasks for the Scryers will cause your Aldor reputation level to decrease.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Manaforge Duro is in trouble? I\'m sure Thalodien will love to hear the news. Let\'s wrap up the job here first.' WHERE `entry`=10198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='How goes the eavesdropping, $N? You\'d best hurry. I\'m getting antsy here.' WHERE `entry`=10198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You do not cease to amaze me, $N. That was quite the feat of stealth you pulled off at Manaforge Coruu.' WHERE `entry`=10200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You tell Rakoria the results of the test and she throws her head back, laughing.>' WHERE `entry`=10201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Well, do you have the test results?' WHERE `entry`=10201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It\'s about time you showed up. I was beginning to wonder if the Scryers were interested at all.' WHERE `entry`=10202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hmmm... just as I suspected.$B$BExposure to this level of raw energy greatly magnifies our innate addiction to magic.$B$BI\'m not surprised Kael gets away with what he does; all his subordinates are basically drunk on this.' WHERE `entry`=10204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did you investigate the bloodgems used by the Sunfury magisters, $N?' WHERE `entry`=10204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Defeat Summoner Kanthin at Manaforge Duro, on the island to the north of Sunfury Hold, and reclaim the Stone of Glacius from him. When you have obtained the stone, use Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff to contact the archmage.$B$BIf you lose Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff, speak to Ravandwyr at Area 52 to receive a replacement.' WHERE `entry`=10209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I hope you learned a thing or two about Shattrath, $N. It might take some time for things to sink in.' WHERE `entry`=10211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The stories of men are ephemeral, $N. The stories of cities last well into the years.' WHERE `entry`=10211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You are truly the hero of the Mag\'har, $N. If not for you, we would have surely been overrun by the ogres and Broken.$B$BWe are a poor people but we do have some artifacts of power. Please, I insist that you take from our coffer.' WHERE `entry`=10212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You close your eyes and press a button.>' WHERE `entry`=10216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Seeing as how this was Morphalius\'s idea, I decided to give him his old job back. Well done little flesh beast. Well done, indeed!$B$BRemember, if you\'re ever looking for work and happen to be in Netherstorm, come find me at the Stormspire.' WHERE `entry`=10218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Hello, little flesh beast.' WHERE `entry`=10218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You\'re not certain, but it seems as though Custodian Dieworth is on the verge of tears.>$B$BAt last, it is through. If I could will myself out of existence, I would, but the truth is I don\'t know how to let go. For the ones in the village, it is difficult but straightforward. I suppose this is the price we pay for retaining such strong ties to this place.' WHERE `entry`=10223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Smoke rises from the Sunfury Hold fortifications. Is that your handiwork?' WHERE `entry`=10233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you saved my peons yet? Please hurry, I\'m afraid they are going to be eaten and they probably won\'t taste very good. If they taste really bad the fel orcs might get really mad at me.' WHERE `entry`=10238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent job, $N. With your dedication we\'re sure to defeat our enemy.' WHERE `entry`=10246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well met, my $Gbrother:sister;. I\'m glad you\'ve come. I am Danath - leader of the Sons of Lothar, and force commander of this hold.' WHERE `entry`=10254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Thiah Redmane\'s eyes widen as you describe the results of the experiment.>$B$BBut, how could that happen? I\'m certain I prepared the antidote correctly!$B$BI\'ve seen it work with spider and snake venoms, so why would it backfire here? Perhaps that\'s one of Outland\'s many peculiarities, $N. I\'d best pass this information along to my comrades.' WHERE `entry`=10255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Amazing! From what little I\'ve seen of the fate of Farahlon, I\'m not certain I want to go outside, but it\'s much better than being trapped here for the rest of my days.' WHERE `entry`=10257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $N. Among the chaos of battle, heroes burn bright against the darkness. Your light shines true!' WHERE `entry`=10259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hello, $R.$B$BYou don\'t happen to be available for a recovery mission of some importance?' WHERE `entry`=10263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hello, $R.$B$BYou don\'t happen to be available for a recovery mission of some importance?' WHERE `entry`=10264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I welcome you to the Stormspire, $C. Please enjoy the hospitality of the Consortium.$B$BYou may place that equipment anywhere. I suspect that you\'ll be picking it back up rather soon.' WHERE `entry`=10268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Dealer Hazzin lowers his voice to a whisper.>$B$BAh, I know of your mission. It is one of great importance to Nexus-Prince Haramad!$B$BNow that we know the location of this first triangulation point, you must move swiftly to find the second!' WHERE `entry`=10269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Hello, traveler. You come to Hazzin because you are in need of my goods?' WHERE `entry`=10269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This power cell should hold for our purposes. Once the money starts rolling in, we\'ll improve it even more.$B$BEnough with such things. Every moment spent in discussion translates to lost profit.' WHERE `entry`=10270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='And to think, that wretched ethereal was going to sell these essences to the blood elves like so much candy...' WHERE `entry`=10271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These will work quite nicely, $N. Thank you for agreeing to help us.$B$BBefore we can continue, however, there is something else we\'ll need to address.' WHERE `entry`=10272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='Your former employer, Wind Trader Marid, must\'ve gotten wind that you\'re helping us now. Through my projection, I\'ve seen his nether-stalkers entering the area, hoping to track us down.$B$BWe\'ve been able evade them so far, but Marid must be dealt with before the problem grows more severe.$B$BIf your impressions of Marid are correct, he\'ll do just about anything to secure the supply of his product. Return to him and tell him you\'re prepared to offer a deal. Lure him away and slay him.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Now that that troublesome ethereal has been dealt with, we can focus our efforts on understanding these nether dragons. I\'ve had a chance to examine the eggs and I\'ve made a few discoveries.' WHERE `entry`=10273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. Well done indeed. The nether dragonkin will not accept a blue dragon among them at first, but with time and the firm demonstration of my authority, they will come around. Scattered, isolated, and without a definitive leader, we must be vigilant in preventing them from falling under the sway of a malevolent power, keeping them in check all the while.' WHERE `entry`=10274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you challenged and defeated Veraku?' WHERE `entry`=10274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Very good indeed. The nexus-prince shall be pleased!$B$BWe now have the second point, which will now tell us where the third is, and the general vicinity of the crystal!' WHERE `entry`=10275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You wish to buy or sell?' WHERE `entry`=10275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Beyond my wildest dreams, I never thought that you would be able to retrieve the crystal!$B$BAnd then to actually give it to me! Do you have any idea how powerful it is?$B$BYour selflessness is inspirational and beyond reproach, $N! You have given me much to think about.' WHERE `entry`=10276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hopefully you now have a better understanding of what is expected of you.' WHERE `entry`=10277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Do not return until you have at least a rudimentary understanding of what is happening.' WHERE `entry`=10277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We must prepare you for the battles that lie ahead...' WHERE `entry`=10279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have recovered Spirit\'s Song!  It is the ata\'mal crystal that Prophet Velen left behind with his people for safekeeping before he went upon his ill-fated mission to the Exodar.$B$BOdd that he did not foresee it falling into the hands of the Burning Legion, if even for a short time.$B$BOr, perhaps he did?  It may be that he foresaw all of this, and left it there so that you would retrieve the crystal and deliver it to me here?$B$BI sense that is the truth of it. You are a great hero of your people, $N!' WHERE `entry`=10280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='My name is Tyrygosa, of the brood of Malygos, but most call me \'Tyri.\' My companion is the $C Jorad Mace.$B$BWord of these strange dragonkin has already traveled far and I fear that too many will rush to exploit them for profit without realizing the true nature of what they\'re dealing with. With your help, we\'re hoping to gain insight into these creatures before others discover their presence.' WHERE `entry`=10281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Our worst fears might soon be realized. The forces at work behind this temporal disturbance are a new flight of dragons known as the Infinite. We do not know where they came from or why they are destroying timeways.$B$BIn this pocket of time, they have kidnapped Taretha Foxton, daughter of Tammis Foxton, the secretary of Aedelas Blackmoore, ruler of Durnholde and overseer of all internment camps on Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=10282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You are friends of Taretha? So this is her new plan? Very well then...' WHERE `entry`=10283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='<Erozion nods.>' WHERE `entry`=10284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Please accept a gift from the bronze flight. These items will assist you in your journeys through time.' WHERE `entry`=10285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Return to Magistrix Carinda at Falcon Watch.' WHERE `entry`=10287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, yes. This is precisely the grade I was hoping for. We may give up mining the crystal formations altogether if we can secure a supply from the giants.' WHERE `entry`=10290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done! I can\'t wait to put this to the test.' WHERE `entry`=10293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$BExcellent. the warp rift generator is almost complete. There is only one final ingredient we require. Soon we shall be able to open up a warp rift to the deepest parts of the abyss. $B$BWho knows what strange creature may come through? Think of it $N. the power such knowledge will bring is limitless.' WHERE `entry`=10294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have done well, $N. The child, Andormu, wishes to speak to you once more.' WHERE `entry`=10297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You may only use one chrono-beacon per pocket of time.' WHERE `entry`=10297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Obtain the Heliotrope Oculus from Spellreaver Marathelle at Sunfury Hold. Use Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff to contact the archmage once you have achieved your goal.$B$BIf you lose Archmage Vargoth\'s Staff, speak to Ravandwyr at Area 52 to receive a replacement.' WHERE `entry`=10301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N, is it? I\'ve heard good things about you and the work you\'ve been doing in the short time since you came to.$B$BWe\'ll definitely need your help getting things back to normal. Zhanaa, over there, could also use your help, I\'m sure.' WHERE `entry`=10304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What have you found, $N?' WHERE `entry`=10305;
