UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='That was fast. You must be a very efficient person to have placed all three of those markers already.' WHERE `entry`=10335;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Truly an exceptional job.$B$BWith the demons of Culuthas slain, Zephyrion will be able to safely take his excavation team into the Ruins of Farahlon.$B$BAccept this coin as a token of my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=10336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That makes three manaforges you\'ve shut down, $N. Kael\'thas must be having a real fit right about now.' WHERE `entry`=10338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did you complete the shut down? You should hurry before I change my mind about the whole deal.' WHERE `entry`=10338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We must gather whatever data that they\'ve stored in this area.' WHERE `entry`=10339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hah hah! A fresh $R from the mainland! Well don\'t worry - Shatter Point might make you queasy but she doesn\'t stray far!$B$BAnd I\'ve only seen her flip upside down once... or twice.' WHERE `entry`=10340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done well, $N. Kael\'s army will not easily recover from the blow you\'ve dealt today.' WHERE `entry`=10341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You spoke with Runetog? A fine dwarf he is. Keeps his gryphons in good shape and battle ready.$B$BI\'m Gryphongar, commander here at Shatter Point. I know it\'s not pretty, but this hunk of rock is a vital staging point for sorties into Hellfire. You\'ll see gryphons flying out and in non-stop!$B$BAdvice? Here\'s some: keep your gear stowed, your stomach empty, and your eye on the horizon... if Shatter Point starts to teeter, then grab onto something that won\'t float away!' WHERE `entry`=10344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You saved my wrappings, $N. The Protectorate will know of what you\'ve done on this day, friend.' WHERE `entry`=10345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Any luck in finding Ya-six?' WHERE `entry`=10345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The other windrider pilots speak highly of you, $N. You\'ve scored quite a lot of kills on the Abyssal Shelf. Keep up the good works!' WHERE `entry`=10347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, so you\'ve finally come. I am Behomat, and I will instruct you in the ways of the $C arts. Ruada told me of your trial against the ravager, and I am impressed. And I have a gift for you.$B$BWhat we have scavenged from the wreckage of the Exodar is little, and must be given to those most able. Please take a weapon suited to your fighting style and carry it with the knowledge you have earned it.$B$BAnd speaking of fighting styles, it\'s time you learned something new.' WHERE `entry`=10350;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='And Ya-six? Did he make it?$B$BLet\'s damn well hope so. I was unable to get reinforcements back to them... Ethereum have the entire area covered now.$B$BMy apologies, I nearly forgot about your reward.' WHERE `entry`=10353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Fantastic - these will go right to use, I assure you. Thank you again for your assistance! We\'d certainly be lost without you.$B$BWith all the donations you\'ve made, I would certainly process any additional runecloth donations you care to make in the future. Just be sure to check in with me, and I\'ll personally make sure that your good deeds won\'t go unrecognized!' WHERE `entry`=10357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N - without heroes like you working on behalf of the tribe, we\'d surely suffer. Thank you for your continued efforts!' WHERE `entry`=10358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Fantastic - these will go right to use, I assure you. Thank you again for your assistance! We\'d certainly be lost without you.$B$BWith all the donations you\'ve made, I would certainly process any additional runecloth donations you care to make in the future. Just be sure to check in with me, and I\'ll personally make sure that your good deeds won\'t go unrecognized!' WHERE `entry`=10362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N - without heroes like you working on behalf of the tribe, we\'d surely suffer. Thank you for your continued efforts!' WHERE `entry`=10363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Burning Legion is in cahoots with Kael? Hah! Voren\'thal is going to have a field day with this information.$B$BDo you think the thousands of pilgrims that have come from Azeroth want to be allied with the Burning Legion? I think not!' WHERE `entry`=10365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I thank you, $N. My people will soon be free thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=10367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I can feel it, $N! The spirits are returning to us.' WHERE `entry`=10368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Tell me, $N. Have the Dreghood elders been released?' WHERE `entry`=10368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I was beginning to wonder if Zelanis received that letter.$B$BGood. Let\'s get to work.' WHERE `entry`=10372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah. good, another has arrived. Time may not matter to me, but to you it is of the essence. There is much for you to learn and there is much I wish to teach you. You simply must prove your worth. Do that, and you shall be greatly rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=10379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is done then. We come here, hunt them down and slay them at the bidding of our masters. No quarter is given or expected.$B$BMakes you wonder sometimes.' WHERE `entry`=10380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The bad news you bring fills my heart with sorrow. Two of our deadliest foes join forces and one of the dearest sons of Shattrath has lost his way.' WHERE `entry`=10381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You hold the data cell out so Ameer can read the plans.>$B$BNothing... Damn them! They\'re clever but not as clever as Ameer!$B$BWhat I\'m about to ask you to do is quite dangerous. I\'ll understand if you don\'t want to continue, fleshling.' WHERE `entry`=10384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Protectorate\'s reason for existence is now fully realized.$B$BThe Ethereum are not here to hunt Dimensius! They are here to become void!$B$BThey are manipulating the void energy at this manaforge to bond their own energy into a creature known as a nexus-stalker.$B$BThey are undoubtedly using a proto-accelerator to complete the transformation.' WHERE `entry`=10385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $C, That\'s one less forge camp we\'ll need to worry about. It\'ll take the Legion a while to get that facility back up and running. You\'ve just bought us the one thing we\'d run out of' WHERE `entry`=10390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I have to hand it to you, $N, you\'re a fighter born! Those Horde yokels may never know how close they came to the end. It takes real character to step in harm\'s way on behalf of your enemies. That\'s the kind of honor and commitment that holds the Alliance together!$B$B<Field Marshal Brock salutes you crisply>' WHERE `entry`=10396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Light be praised, I knew you\'d do it! Arazzius and his minions are no more! Soon, we\'ll have the Legion running for home and this battered world will be safe once more. Then, when justice has been met, we can return home as well.$B$BThanks you, $N - the Alliance and the Sons of Lothar honor you this day!' WHERE `entry`=10400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve dealt a mighty blow to the enemies of the Light, $N. You have my thanks as well as that of the Aldor.' WHERE `entry`=10404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! Now to calibrate the device.' WHERE `entry`=10405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thanks to you, their plans are in ruin! Now only one thing remains... Salhadaar.' WHERE `entry`=10406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='He must succeed!' WHERE `entry`=10406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your dedication to our cause is exemplary, $N. With Socrethar\'s teleportation stone in our possession only one thing remains to be done.' WHERE `entry`=10407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It has been a thousand years, maybe more, since Salhadaar began his crusade to exterminate all that would stand in his way. I can hardly believe that this is the last we\'ll see of him... You have done all of us a great service, $N, and for that you will be rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=10408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is done, $N. Socrethar has been destroyed.$B$BI and the others will recover from our wounds, $N. The wrath of Socrethar\'s magic was far too much for young Kaylaan, however. Not even my strongest prayer could raise him.$B$BIt is an unbearable pity that one so young would fall in battle. However, in the end his will was strong enough to recover from the Legion\'s corruption and we may find solace in that.' WHERE `entry`=10409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Socrethar... I remember that name. He was once a renowned warrior of the Light and pride was his only flaw.' WHERE `entry`=10410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I hope it\'s not too late. Did you notice any abnormally large slimes at or near the area where the void wastes drain into?' WHERE `entry`=10411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. You might prove to be a useful ally after all.' WHERE `entry`=10412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='WHAT!? You faced off against a void horror? And lived?! Incredible!$B$BThis sample is worth its weight in gold. A find like this deserves a reward.' WHERE `entry`=10413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes... Kael\'s numbers continue to dwindle as our numbers continue to grow.' WHERE `entry`=10414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent!  All who oppose us will be crushed!' WHERE `entry`=10415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='As promised, $N. The entirety of the book\'s raw power, condensed into a single rune.' WHERE `entry`=10416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The power contained in this tome is tremendous. Yet it is easily condensed into a single rune by one with a clear mind.' WHERE `entry`=10419;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Watch as foul materials disintegrate. Watch as metal turns to dust.$B$BThe Light cleanses all and only the purest residue remains.' WHERE `entry`=10420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The fel materials are removed from this world. Only the Light\'s residue remains.' WHERE `entry`=10421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $N. Tyralius suffered massive injuries but we think he\'s going to make it.$B$BHe mentioned fields of prisons, much like the one you rescued him from. Prisons full of creatures from all across the universe!$B$BWe\'ll be in touch should a need arise to crack those open. The Consortium has already expressed some interest in sending some teams out and is working on some technology to break through the Ethereum\'s locks.' WHERE `entry`=10422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did you find Tyralius?' WHERE `entry`=10422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Speak with Ghabar at the Stormspire.' WHERE `entry`=10423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Commander Ameer appears pleased.>$B$BWell done, fleshling! This soldier might be the key to taking down the Ethereum\'s entire operation.' WHERE `entry`=10425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh my! Focusing the dome\'s energy seems to continue accelerating growth to the point where it breeds extreme aggression. If we do get the ability to use this technology, we have to be sure to calibrate it correctly.' WHERE `entry`=10426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Did you try focusing the dome\'s energy?' WHERE `entry`=10426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent work. I\'ll keep a close eye on the ones you tagged and see if they mature as quickly as the other lifeforms in the dome.$B$BWith the proper control, we could use this technology to regrow the ruined areas of Outland and Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=10427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Were you able to tag enough of the talbuk?' WHERE `entry`=10427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Even for a creature of that size, this heart is far too large. It struggled to keep up with the creature\'s gigantic body. I have little doubt it would\'ve died before reaching half its normal lifespan.$B$BEven with such risks, I\'m determined to convince the Consortium to share their technology. There\'s too much promise here to give up now.' WHERE `entry`=10429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Bring the Repair Apparatus to Tashar at Eco-Dome Farfield.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='This looks a little peculiar. Ghabar definitely didn\'t have Netherstorm in mind when he designed it.$B$BDon\'t look so surprised, $N. Netherstorm is tame compared to some of the environments I\'ve worked in. Nevertheless, a failing dome is always a concern.' WHERE `entry`=10430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'re all the help Orelis is sending? He must think very highly of you.$B$BLet\'s get this over with.' WHERE `entry`=10431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is big, $N. Very big!$B$BVoren\'thal is going to want to hear about this as soon as possible.' WHERE `entry`=10432;
