UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent work! The most difficult part of the project is done. Now, all we need is a way to get these back to Area 52 and attract the interest of the Cenarion Expedition as well. There should be enough here for our own needs and to earn a little profit on the side.' WHERE `entry`=10435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done. It looks like everything is in order. We\'re ready to begin.' WHERE `entry`=10436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent. With these fragments, we can calibrate a bomb that will destroy the void conduit atop Ultris. With the void conduit destroyed, Dimensius\'s connection with the void will be severed and he will be left defenseless!' WHERE `entry`=10437;
