UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Allow me to reward you for undertaking such an arduous task, hero.$B$BNow, we must get to work! Please stand back so that I may place the totem and unleash the souls.' WHERE `entry`=10481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Soon, we will speak with the spirits.' WHERE `entry`=10481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Gor\'drek has asked you to slay 12 Bladewing Bloodletters. Return to him at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains once you have accomplished that.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='That didn\'t take as long as I thought it would. Are you sure that you dealt with as many as was necessary?$B$BVery well, there\'s something else that I want you to help us with. Something far more important.' WHERE `entry`=10486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Gor\'drek wants you to gather 4 Dusts of the Fey Drake. After doing so, return to him at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use Gor\'drek\'s Ointment on 5 of the Thunderlord Dire Wolves to strengthen them and the defense of the Jagged Ridge. Then return to Gor\'drek at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='WANTED!$B$BStronglimb Deeproot, ancient of war and chief defender of the Living Grove south of Sylvanaar.$B$BFind him by heading west across the bridge that traverses the Bloodmaul Ravine.$B$BReturn his hewn trunk to Tor\'chunk Twoclaws inside the Thunderlord Stronghold inn.',`objectives_loc8`='Acquire Stronglimb Deeproot\'s Trunk and deliver it to Tor\'chunk Twoclaws at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We meet again. I have been watching your progress from afar, $C, and I am pleased.$B$BThe time has come for you to commune with the element of water, to learn its mysteries and give yourself over to the water so that you might in turn learn to master it.' WHERE `entry`=10490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='And finally we come to it, the last of the four great elements: air. Do you think yourself wise enough to continue, $N?' WHERE `entry`=10491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! Let\'s perform the trade then. It\'s hard to part with this excellent armor, but I\'m afraid I won\'t be needing it any time soon.$B$BIf you\'re interested in performing more work for me, I might be willing to give up the rest of the pieces.' WHERE `entry`=10492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, yes. Mux will be quite happy with this.$B$BThose bracers were part of a larger armor set. If you\'re interested in providing me with further assistance, I\'d be willing to consider parting with the rest of it.' WHERE `entry`=10493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve kept your end of the bargain, I shall keep mine.$B$BJust remember that I\'m holding on to the best pieces until your work is finished.' WHERE `entry`=10494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Our agreement remains in place. Just remember, this is but a taste of what awaits you. Free me of this cursed fate and I will reward you with items of truly great power.' WHERE `entry`=10495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Throm\'ka, $C! Good to see so many of the Horde, such as yourself, $N, coming out to lend your support in laying the groundwork for the upcoming Ahn\'Qiraj War. The effort here will ensure that we are victorious against the Silithid and their evil masters hidden away inside Ahn\'Qiraj.$B$BSo now that you are here, be sure to speak with the various collectors and offer your assistance in gathering those materials that you are suited to.' WHERE `entry`=10500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Commander Skyshadow has tasked you with the destruction of any 30 Bloodmaul Ogres at Bloodmaul Outpost. Return to him at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains once your gruesome task is completed.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is a good first step toward securing Sylvanaar and the grove.$B$BWith their ogres not so numerous, the Bloodmaul will think twice about attacking us here.$B$BNow, if only they were the only clan of ogres that we have to worry about.' WHERE `entry`=10502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Our scouts have reported that the Bloodmaul ogres have begun to creep up the switchback, which leads up to the Living Grove from their hold.$B$BIt is unfortunate that we cannot find a way to live together in peace with the ogres, but then, when have we ever been able to do so?' WHERE `entry`=10502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Tor\'chunk Twoclaws has tasked you with the destruction of any 30 Bladespire Ogres and 10 Bladespire Raptors at Bladespire Hold and the Bladespire Grounds. Return to him at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains once your task is completed.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is a good first step toward securing our position here against the ogres.$B$BWith their numbers decimated, the Bladespire will think twice about attempting to retake Thunderlord Stronghold.$B$BNow, if they were the only clan of ogres that we have to worry about.' WHERE `entry`=10503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Our scouts have reported that the Bladespire ogres have established a camp even closer to the switchback, which leads from their hold up to us here.$B$BIt is unfortunate that we cannot simply subjugate these ogre scum to our will, but if it\'s a fight that they want, they will find the Horde more than accommodating.' WHERE `entry`=10503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='You have been asked by Commander Skyshadow to kill any 30 Bladespire Ogres in Bladespire Hold and the Bladespire Grounds. Return to him at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains once you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your actions against both the Bloodmaul and the Bladespire ogre clans have gone a long way to securing Sylvanaar\'s future. While we do not seek to expand past this patch of land, which we initially found empty, we will also not suffer those that would destroy us.$B$BAs you have done us good service, I would reward that service with the appreciation of the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=10504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Bloodmaul or Bladespire, it doesn\'t matter. All of the ogre clans fight against each other, vying for the dominance that comes with having the favor of Gruul the Dragonkiller.$B$BEach is still our enemy, regardless of who that favor has fallen to.' WHERE `entry`=10504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='You have been asked by Tor\'chunk Twoclaws to kill any 30 Bloodmaul Ogres at Bloodmaul Outpost. Return to him at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains once you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your actions against both the Bladespire and the Bloodmaul ogre clans have gone a long way to securing Thunderlord Stronghold\'s future. We will not suffer those that would get in the way of our destiny here.$B$BAs you have done good work in destroying these ogres, I intend to reward you with the appreciation of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=10505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Bladespire or Bloodmaul, it matters not. All of the ogre clans fight against each other, vying for the dominance that comes with having the favor of Gruul the Dragonkiller.$B$BEach is still our enemy, regardless of who that favor has fallen to, and we will drive them before us!' WHERE `entry`=10505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Rina Moonspring wants you to take her Diminution Powder and apply it to 5 of the Bloodmaul Dire Wolves, which can be found at Bloodmaul Outpost and in Bloodmaul Ravine. After doing so, return to her at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m glad to hear that it worked. The fewer the number of Nature\'s creatures that have to die, the better.$B$BWith all that you\'ve done for us already, I must say that I\'m beginning to grow very fond of your company.$B$BTake care, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Any luck out there? I know that it\'s dangerous work to be doing this amongst the Bloodmaul ogres, but if we can avoid the killing of any more animals, I\'ll be happy.' WHERE `entry`=10506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You are an individual of formidable power, $N. The Scryers are fortunate to count you as an ally.$B$BAs word of Kael\'s new allegiance spreads, more people will see things our way. The fact that we can claim such a decisive victory against Kael\'thas\' new overlords puts us in a most favorable situation.$B$BI will not forget your deeds.' WHERE `entry`=10507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You do not cease to amaze me, $N!  Good thing you\'re on our side.' WHERE `entry`=10508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have no idea what this will mean for the Scryers, $N. You will have to excuse me while I catch my breath and assess the situation.' WHERE `entry`=10509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Bronwyn Stouthammer has asked you to collect 5 Draenethyst Mine Crystals and then return to her at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ooh, by the looks of those, they\'re fine specimens. I can\'t wait to get my examination tools unpacked and have a real look at them!$B$BThank you!' WHERE `entry`=10510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Borgrim Stouthammer wants you to procure 11 Bloodmaul Brutebane Brew for him. Once you\'ve done that, return it to him at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='What is that smell?  Oh no, don\'t tell me that\'s the ogre brew?!$B$BI\'m almost afraid to try this stuff out. Oh well, what the hell?  Bottoms up!' WHERE `entry`=10511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Take the Bloodmaul Brutebane Keg and use it in an attempt to get 5 Bladespire Ogres drunk. If you\'re successful, return to Borgrim at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, hahaha! That\'s what I thought. I guess ogre\'s will drink anything.$B$BStupid, the lot of \'em!$B$BWell, I must say even though I didn\'t get my brew, you have given me a great start to my vacation.$B$BTell you what... we have all sorts of stuff here we don\'t really need. Can I offer you something?' WHERE `entry`=10512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What\'s the word? Are the Bladespire ogres as indiscriminate as the Bloodmaul, or did it nearly kill them like it did me?' WHERE `entry`=10512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Words of damnation? Never heard of \'em. Take my advice: Let the dead rest.$B$BBut since you\'ve already come all this way, I could use some help with a few other matters. What do you say?' WHERE `entry`=10513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You say there were a lot more of those flayers than you expected? Looks like it\'s time to take out the trash.' WHERE `entry`=10514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That\'ll teach those damned, filthy animals not to kill my boars! Well done, $N!' WHERE `entry`=10515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Retrieve Vindicator Vuuleen\'s Blade and Vindicator Vuuleen\'s Shield. Then return them to Vindicator Vuuleen at Bladespire Hold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='And now I owe you a great debt, for you have helped me to restore my honor. But our work here is not yet over.' WHERE `entry`=10516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Vindicator Vuuleen has asked you to kill Gorr\'Dim, leader of the Bladespire Hold ogres. Once you have done so, return to her at Bladespire Hold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Very well. You\'re a very resourceful $C, that\'s for certain.$B$BI wonder then if there\'s one more thing that you can do for myself and Sylvanaar?' WHERE `entry`=10517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use the Bladespire Banner atop the Northmaul Tower to lure Gurn Grubnosh. Deliver the banner and the Helm of Gurn Grubnosh to Commander Skyshadow at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Gurn Grubnosh\'s helm and a Bladespire banner?$B$BQuite clever of you and the vindicator to come up with that plan.$B$BBy keeping the attention of the Bloodmaul clan on Bladespire Hold, you\'ve relieved the pressure that they were beginning to assert upon us here.$B$BPlease, $N, accept a humble gift from Sylvanaar.' WHERE `entry`=10518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Do you understand what must be done? Find the sons of Oronok. Find my boys...' WHERE `entry`=10519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Be patient and listen, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Grom\'tor grunts.>$B$BIt\'s good you came. This maggot just spilled its guts. We\'ve got them now!' WHERE `entry`=10521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This must be taken back to father at once.' WHERE `entry`=10522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='When the Cipher of Damnation is reformed, we shall end this curse!' WHERE `entry`=10523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Retrieve the Thunderlord Clan Drum, Thunderlord Clan Arrow and the Thunderlord Clan Tablet. Return them, along with the Thunderlord Clan Artifact, to Rokgah Bloodgrip at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='I do not believe my eyes! If this is some sort of trick, I will flay the flesh from your bones, $C!$B$BQuickly, let me examine these priceless artifacts before you break them with your clumsy hands.' WHERE `entry`=10524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use the Fiery Soul Fragment to transform your spirit into a vision guide. Speak with Rokgah Bloodgrip at Thunderlord Stronghold after your vision has guided you to the location of the final Thunderlord relic.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='The back of the Draenethyst Mine? The Bloodmaul clan must have stolen it from the Bladespire ogres.$B$BBah! That is too far away... too deep into Bloodmaul territory for me to travel.$B$BBut you. You know the path. You will go there in my stead!' WHERE `entry`=10525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What did you see? Tell me, I must know where it is!' WHERE `entry`=10525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Rokgah Bloodgrip has tasked you with the retrieval of the Thunderspike. Return it to her at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Now I am impressed! Do you have any idea how many others died attempting to retrieve all of these relics?$B$BWe are fortunate to have you working with us here, $N. Even if you are a bit slow.$B$BYou must allow me to reward your dedication to our cause. Choose, but choose wisely. When you are done, I will hand over the artifacts to appease the ghosts of Thunderlord Stronghold.' WHERE `entry`=10526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ar\'tor\'s body lies limp, suspended in mid-air. You have no idea how long he has been dead but your heart aches for Oronok.$B$BPerhaps you should try and get him down and take his corpse back to his father.' WHERE `entry`=10527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You slide the crystalline key into the slots at the base of each of the demonic crystals.' WHERE `entry`=10528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N, it is good you have come. Our list of allies grows thin, and even those who share our cause are not completely trusted. It is because of this that we, the rangers, turn to nature for aid.$B$BIn the allies of the forest we find a deep bond that does not know deceit.' WHERE `entry`=10529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N, it is good you have come. Our list of allies grows thin, and even those who share our cause are not completely trusted. It is because of this that we, the rangers, turn to nature for aid.$B$BIn the allies of the forest we find a deep bond that does not know deceit.' WHERE `entry`=10530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It means "hero\'s sojourn" in my native tongue. It rings true even now - in this era where our heroes have all died...$B$BIt seems as though one always rises.' WHERE `entry`=10537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Ar\'tor fades in and out of existence.>$B$BIt would seem that my time is nearly at an end, hero.' WHERE `entry`=10540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Oronok wipes the tear away and smiles at you.>$B$BThank you. I promise you, hero, a song of honor will be written in your name.' WHERE `entry`=10541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Retrieve T\'chali\'s Hookah and 10 Bloodmaul Brutebane Brews. Bring them back to T\'chali the Witch Doctor at Bloodmaul Ravine in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='T\'chali the Witch Doctor has asked you to kill his chief tormentors, Grimnok Battleborn and Korgaah. After you have done so, return to him at Bloodmaul Ravine in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use the Wicked Strong Fetish to curse 5 buildings or towers in Bladespire Hold and 2 in Bloodmaul Outpost. Return to T\'chali the Witch Doctor at Bloodmaul Ravine in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains after you have done so.' WHERE `entry`=10544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='T\'chali has asked you to take the Bloodmaul Brutebane Keg and use it in an attempt to get 5 Bladespire Ogres drunk. If successful, return to T\'chali the Witch Doctor at Bloodmaul Ravine in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Borak is silent for a moment.>$B$BI\'ve been watching these blood elves for weeks now, trying to get a lock on where they\'ve hidden the third part of the Cipher of Damnation.$B$BThus far, I\'ve been unsuccessful in gathering any clues. The only thing I do know is that Illidan sends an envoy from the Black Temple here once a day.$B$BThis envoy is untouchable. I\'ve shadowed him for a week, trying to figure out how to separate him from his bodyguard. Unfortunately, the bodyguard never leaves his side.' WHERE `entry`=10546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve got a rotten arakkoa egg? Well why didn\'t you say so! I think we can do business.$B$B<Tobias smiles, exposing a mouthful of decay and filth.>' WHERE `entry`=10547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, wow. That is not pretty. I\'m sure the merchant will appreciate it more than me.$B$BAs payment, the merchant offered to buy one of my special stock items for you, so take your pick sweetie!' WHERE `entry`=10548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Now to set the trap!' WHERE `entry`=10550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Are you certain of your choice, $N? $BThe Aldor will welcome you as an ally, but the Scryers will not easily forgive your decision.' WHERE `entry`=10551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Are you certain of your choice, $N? $BThe Scryers will welcome you as an ally, but the Aldor will not easily forgive your decision.' WHERE `entry`=10552;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Khadgar sends a new recruit? Let us put you to work, $C.' WHERE `entry`=10553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Collect 18 Plucked Lashh\'an Feathers, then read the Lashh\'an Tome in the treetops of Veil Lashh.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Flipping through the pages of the scratched notes and spindly script of the Lashh\'an arrakoa, you find a page with a pictogram of the circles of power you have seen in Veil Lashh.' WHERE `entry`=10555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use the Fistful of Feathers on the Lashh\'an Spell Circle, then return to Daranelle at Sylvanaar before the kaliri spirit fades.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='I don\'t know what to say. This spell is very strange. It is not a simple conjuration or enchantment, but some sort of communion or communication spell.$B$BI\'m not sure what to make of it, $N. I\'ll have to think about it some more.$B$BBut thanks for your help, anyways! I\'m sure I\'ll think through this sooner or later.$BGains.' WHERE `entry`=10556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='This is exciting! I can\'t wait to examine the workings of the spell.' WHERE `entry`=10556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Speak with Rally Zapnabber and use the Zephyrium Capacitorium. Return to Tally Zapnabber at Toshley\'s Station.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Wow, you made it! And not a single bruise or compound fracture! See, I told you everything would work out!$B$BHere\'s your pay, $N, though I factored in medical expenses and you don\'t need those... so that\'s a bonus for you!' WHERE `entry`=10557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Don\'t be afraid! This is for science, and science is painful!' WHERE `entry`=10557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<A\'dal appears to be extremely pleased with you. With your help Tempest Keep will one day reclaimed from the clutches of evil.>' WHERE `entry`=10560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you for relieving my men, $N. With your help, and that of others, we may yet hold out. Unfortunately, merely holding out is not enough. We must go on the offensive.' WHERE `entry`=10562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='The fortress of Legion Hold is nigh impregnable, and to be completely honest, I can\'t spare the forces for an assault. Our hopes are riding on you, $N.$B$BWhat little information we\'ve been able to gather indicates that the Legion stocks and prepares its infernals at the hold. With the help of a disguise I\'ll give you, you must sneak into Legion Hold and learn about the their plans. Your best hope is to intercept or overhear communication between their commanders. Good luck, $N.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Wing Commander Nuainn listens to your report, growing more alarmed with each sentence.>$B$BSo you\'re saying they have more than enough infernals to intensify the bombardment? If we don\'t stop them before they can put the next phase of their plan into motion, Wildhammer Stronghold is finished.' WHERE `entry`=10563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N! I wish I could say that the Legion would give up after a setback like this, but you and I know better than that. The Deathforge that you learned about during your reconnaissance mission will be our next target.' WHERE `entry`=10564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you found a way to destroy the Legion\'s infernal stockpile?' WHERE `entry`=10564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Collect and use a Vekh\'nir Crystal at the Vekh\'nir Spell Circle, then return the Charged Vekh\'nir Crystal to Dertrok at the Mok\'Nathal Village.' WHERE `entry`=10565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Try out each of Dertrok\'s wands on an Arakkoa Ogre Slave, then return to Dertrok. Each wand will require an Infused Vekh\'nir Crystal to use.' WHERE `entry`=10566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I eagerly await your results, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Find 6 Ruuan\'ok Claws and use them at the Ruaan\'ok Oracle Circle to summon a Harbinger of the Raven. Kill it and return its Harbinger\'s Pendant to Timeon at Ruuan Weald.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have it!$B$BWith this pendant, I will be able to attune you to the arakkoa of Grishnath in such a way that will enable you to comprehend their speech.$B$BWith this, we may gain further understanding of the arakkoa, and the nature of the Raven. I will need your help to do this.' WHERE `entry`=10567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Kieran leafs through the journal pages.>$B$BMuch of this is unintelligible. but I can make out bits here and there about preparations for a spell gone awry. casualties, and a deteriorating situation. There\'s also a curious note here about a \'deserter.\'' WHERE `entry`=10569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Borak takes the missive from you and begins to read.>$B$BClever bastards! This is a directive from Illidan that dictates where the cipher is to be hidden next. Apparently, they keep it moving. It does not tell us where it currently rests... If only we could deliver the missive now that we know the next location.$B$BToo bad the seal on the missive is broken, rendering it unusable.$B$BHrm... Yet...' WHERE `entry`=10570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Akama\'s very own handwriting. It is truly sad to think of what became of one as wise and beloved as he.' WHERE `entry`=10571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The wing commander inserts the power core into the armor plates and seals the device shut, nodding.>$B$BThis should do the trick. Should make quite an explosion too, if I do say so m\'self.' WHERE `entry`=10572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The dwarf nods.>$B$BIt\'ll be good to have the backup. We\'ve gathered some preliminary information on what the Shadow Council is up to in there, but I\'ll feel better once we\'re able to start taking action against them.' WHERE `entry`=10573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes! The four fragments of the medallion. Now to put them together...' WHERE `entry`=10574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We\'ve been expecting you, $N. Akama said you would arrive sooner or later.' WHERE `entry`=10575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. I hope you are a good actor. The next step in my grand plan is going to require some theatrics!' WHERE `entry`=10576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Now all you need to do is go get the cipher. Easy, right?' WHERE `entry`=10577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The disguise is delicate. Almost any action, aside from walking, will disrupt the magic holding it together.' WHERE `entry`=10577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Finally! The cipher fragment is ours!$B$B<Borak places the fragment into a box.>' WHERE `entry`=10578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='As soon as all three of the fragments of the cipher are together, the ancient words will be known.$B$BRecovery of this fragment was no doubt challenging. You must be rewarded for such heroism.' WHERE `entry`=10579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Commander Skyshadow has asked you to look in the southern area of the Jagged Ridge of the Blade\'s Edge Mountains for a clue as to the whereabouts of Toshley and the other gnomes.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='SYLVANAAR? COMMANDER SKYSHADOW?$B$BTHIS DOES NOT COMPUTE!$B$BBACK AWAY BEFORE I AM FORCED TO PLAY LOUD SOUNDS AT YOU!' WHERE `entry`=10580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='In a round-about way, R-3D0 has informed you that if you follow the trail of spare parts up the ramp here to the Razor Ridge, you will find the gnomes at a place named Toshley\'s Station.$B$BIf you find him, speak with Toshley.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Alright, you want to make yourself useful? Good, I have just the thing that you can prove yourself with.$B$BI think you\'ll like it.' WHERE `entry`=10581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I wish I could\'ve been out there with you! I\'ve been itching to put my hammer to use, but my mission is to observe, not to kill.$B$BNow that you\'ve punched a hole in their defenses, let\'s get to work on shutting down production in the Deathforge.' WHERE `entry`=10582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Ewan shakes his head as he accepts the pack from you>$B$BI don\'t think Flanis realized how heavily guarded the Deathforge would be. Now that we know what\'s really going on there, I don\'t blame them. I just wish Flanis had known that when he went in.$B$BI can only hope there\'s something here that will help us shut down the Deathforge once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=10583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Toshley has asked you to take the Protovoltaic Magneto Collector and gather up 5 Electromentals. Return to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains after you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! With all of this power that you\'ve recovered we\'ll be able to keep the machinery running for a little while, anyway.$B$BThe Zephyrium Capacitorium is a real pig when it comes to power consumption!$B$BI hope dealing with those electromentals wasn\'t too difficult. I have something else in mind for you to do, and I have a feeling that it\'s going to be a little more dangerous.' WHERE `entry`=10584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='This line of research we have going with the electromentals is exciting! Just think of it... intelligent electrical creatures that we can create at will and that will follow our every instruction!' WHERE `entry`=10584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. Disrupting the Shadow Council\'s summoning puts us one step closer to shutting down the Deathforge.' WHERE `entry`=10585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='We cannot afford to let their production continue. Have you put an end to the summoning ritual?' WHERE `entry`=10585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You make your report to the wing commander and hand over the captured orders.>$B$BDefeating Warbringer Razuun should\'ve meant the end of our troubles with the Legion, but these orders outline a much larger plan that I had anticipated. I fear that more remains to be done.' WHERE `entry`=10586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let\'s take a closer look at these weapons, $N. Hmmm... this is rather unsettling.' WHERE `entry`=10587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='How many times has this spell has been used in the history of our worlds? Undoubtedly, its power for destruction is unparalleled.$B$BWhat you must do now is take the cipher, now made whole, and read from it at the Altar of Damnation - where the memory of Gul\'dan stands.$B$BWhat you will see once the words are uttered are the memories left imprinted upon the land. Stand your ground and await the coming of Cyrukh.$B$BYou must be victorious, $N. This land can not withstand another shattering.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Earthmender Torlok takes the Cipher of Damnation from you.>$B$BYou have done as the elements asked. For that, we are grateful. While you will be rewarded, trouble still looms. The spirits of fire are in turmoil. A claim has been made. The Cipher of Damnation is known by another.$B$BIt is cryptic, I know, but that is all that the spirits would have me know. That and this symbol...$B$B<Earthmender Torlok turns around and points to the sky.>$B$BWhat could it mean?' WHERE `entry`=10588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let me see if I can find out how this works...' WHERE `entry`=10589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Very good, $N. Perhaps you have a taste for revenge after all.' WHERE `entry`=10590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These stones carry a taint I do not wish to remember, but one I cannot forget. You try my patience dangerously by bringing these to me.$B$BHowever, it is clear your heart seeks the same vengeance as I, and I will aid you with instruction.' WHERE `entry`=10592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Banshee Queen has guided you well. This is precisely what I need to combine the fragments.$B$B<Mehlar watches as the vine interweaves through the fragments, binding them together.>$B$BThere!  Scourgebane, I shall call it. Be wary when you use it, for it serves you against its will.' WHERE `entry`=10593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Nickwinkle the Metro-Gnome wants you to place the Oscillating Frequency Scanners in such a way that when you stand amongst them, you are hit by five overlapping Oscillation fields.$B$BReturn to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains after you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, this is extraordinary! I had no idea... it\'s almost as if those crystals are alive.$B$BI wonder if there\'s some sort of symbiotic relationship between them and the nether drakes?$B$BThank you, thank you! You must accept a little something from my collection of odds and ends that I wouldn\'t be caught dead wearing.$B$BOne of them might look good on you, though.' WHERE `entry`=10594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Well, do you have the measurements from the singing crystals that I asked for?' WHERE `entry`=10594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m impressed that you managed to survive the carnage. You just might be the person we need for a dangerous mission.' WHERE `entry`=10595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='What do you mean they\'re going to step up the bombardment? We can\'t allow that to happen. Get back out there and take care of it while there\'s something left of Shadowmoon Village!' WHERE `entry`=10596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That should do the trick. I wouldn\'t want to be in the hold when that thing goes off.' WHERE `entry`=10597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is no time for celebration, $N. We\'re not out of the fire yet. I\'ve got new orders for you.' WHERE `entry`=10598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you found a way to destroy the Legion\'s infernal stockpile?' WHERE `entry`=10598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The orc nods.>$B$BIt\'ll be good to have the backup. We\'ve gathered some preliminary information on what the Shadow Council is up to in there, but it\'s time for the hammer to fall.' WHERE `entry`=10599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'d\'ve been down there cracking skulls myself, but I\'m under strict orders not to engage the enemy.$B$BLet\'s get to work on shutting down production in there.' WHERE `entry`=10600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Zagran shakes his head as he accepts the pack from you>$B$BI told you he was a fool. I hope there\'s something in here that justifies the time you spent searching for him.' WHERE `entry`=10601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Good, we\'re making progress. That puts us one step closer to shutting down this facility and returning safely to Shadowmoon Village.' WHERE `entry`=10602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='We cannot afford to let their production continue. Have you put an end to the summoning ritual?' WHERE `entry`=10602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<You make your report to the blood guard and hand over the captured orders.>$B$BGood work, $N, but don\'t go thinking you\'ll be getting any ribbons for it. Let the night elves decorate their pretty little uniforms if they wish. Real warriors share tales of battle over a mug of ale.' WHERE `entry`=10603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='At last, we have a means with which to drive the Legion from Shadowmoon!' WHERE `entry`=10604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, yet another power hungry initiate. Wonderful!$B$BWouldn\'t be much of a $C if you didn\'t thirst for power, now would you boy? Let\'s get on with it.' WHERE `entry`=10605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ah, this is exactly what we\'ll need. I\'d never accuse the Legion of producing anything resembling literature, but it gets the job done.' WHERE `entry`=10606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill Grishna arakkoa to gain Understanding Ravenspeech for 2 minutes. While under the effects of the spell, you can find and receive the prophecy from the four shrines. Return when you have visited all four.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is truly disturbing. The arakkoa were peaceful for a long time. This cult of the Raven was nothing more than a gathering of misfits and madmen.$B$BBut their power has grown, that we cannot discount. Perhaps there is more to this Raven than we know.' WHERE `entry`=10607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What is this $N? What do they believe he will do? Where do they believe he will lead them?' WHERE `entry`=10607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Nickwinkle the Metro-Gnome wants you to slay 10 Crystal Flayers and then return to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Good riddance to them; that\'s what I say. Filthy creatures!$B$BSo, if you\'re certain that you eliminated those pests, then I have a little research project for you. I think you\'ll like it.' WHERE `entry`=10608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Collect 3 Proto-Nether Drake Essences, 3 Adolescent Drake Essences and 3 Mature Drake Essences. Return with them to Fizit "Doc" Clocktock at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve no idea how important this research could be. Thank you!$B$BIt\'ll be interesting to delve into these essences. I\'m particularly curious to see if the nether effect that changed the black dragon eggs into nether dragon eggs resulted in any potential extra blessings for my studies.$B$BI\'m thinking, in fact, that you should be the first person to test out the benefits of my little concoction. Here, take these preliminary samples and use them when you find the need.' WHERE `entry`=10609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This has the information I\'m looking for. Just a couple more tweaks, and we\'ll have you taking control of a fel reaver in no time.' WHERE `entry`=10611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Amazing! You\'ve managed to do what all the gryphonriders in Wildhammer Stronghold couldn\'t! You\'ve broken the back of the Burning Legion\'s advance and spared us from annihilation at the hands of their infernals. You have our deepest gratitude for your service, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You\'re back, so I\'ll assume the operation went well. What\'ve you got to report?' WHERE `entry`=10612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'ll admit it, $N. I\'m impressed by all you\'ve managed to accomplish. Destroying the Legion\'s ability to make war in Shadowmoon will give us the opportunity to turn the tide elsewhere.' WHERE `entry`=10613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='You\'re back, so I\'ll assume the operation went well. What\'ve you got to report?' WHERE `entry`=10613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Search out Leoroxx at the Mok\'Nathal Village in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='What brings you to our village?' WHERE `entry`=10614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Taerek at Mok\'Nathal Village wants you to collect 8 Silkwing Cocoons from Silkwing Larva.$B$BKill the Larva quickly or they will turn into Silkwings, ruining their cocoons.' WHERE `entry`=10617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Silmara at Mok\'Nathal Village wants you to collect 12 Iridescent Wings.' WHERE `entry`=10618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Glory to the naaru, $N. You\'ve done the Light\'s bidding by defeating those who follow Illidan.' WHERE `entry`=10619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Dizzy Dina wants you to kill 10 Ridgespine Stalkers. After you have done so, return to her at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Pretty good for a rookie. As it turns out, we\'ve got a small group of eggheads that want to go \'observe\' the ethereals and their technology up north. They\'ll be thrilled to know that you cleared the way for them.$B$BHere, take some of these. We don\'t have many, but maybe they\'ll help you out in the future.' WHERE `entry`=10620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Ordinn accepts the weapon fragment from you.>$B$BI haven\'t seen something like this in a long time. Sure, it\'s made from a rare ore, but this is destined for no mundane weapon, $N. It\'s infused with a magic intended to destroy demons. If you obtained this from the Legion, it must be some kind of \'secret weapon\' they\'re planning to deploy against Illidan. What a find!' WHERE `entry`=10621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Very well, $N. Your allegiance is no longer in question. You may see Akama now.' WHERE `entry`=10622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Grokom accepts the weapon fragment from you.>$B$BI haven\'t seen this in years. Not only is it made from a rare ore. but it\'s not about to be used in an ordinary weapon, $N.$B$BThese runes imbue the blade with the power to obliterate demons. This shows how much the Legion hates Illidan, if they\'re willing to arm their own troops with demon-destroying weapons. We could use this to our advantage.' WHERE `entry`=10623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Your world is about to change, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Gorefiend? T... Teron Gorefiend? But... How?$B$BHow could Gorefiend be here? This is impossible!$B$BThe legend of Teron Gorefiend is one that causes even the Forsaken to tremble in fear. By all accounts, Gorefiend was a warlock of Gul\'dan' WHERE `entry`=10625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These should work nicely. Now, let\'s forge them into a more useful form.' WHERE `entry`=10626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These should work nicely. Now, let\'s forge them into a more useful form.' WHERE `entry`=10627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hail, $N. There is much we need to talk about.$B$BI hope your mind is an open one. The decisions I make are not understood by many. Only my closest collaborators have understanding of the portents I see and the signs I await.$B$BWhen I joined forces with Illidan it was based on visions foretelling that otherwise my race would have been destroyed. I\'ve waited patiently for other signs and visions to come to pass... Velen\'s exodus... the opening of the Dark Portal... and now... your arrival.' WHERE `entry`=10628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Razak Ironsides has asked you to gather up 5 Extra Sharp Daggermaw Teeth. Return them to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Good work, kid. All of the pain is worth it if even one of my soldiers\' lives is saved by your efforts.$B$BI think you should benefit from your sweat and tears, too. Since we\'re going to have a new batch of weapons soon, why don\'t you take one of mine?' WHERE `entry`=10632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Gorefiend? Why, I have not heard that name in ages!$B$BAfter the Second War, Gorefiend returned here, along with his death knights. Unable to cope with the terrible nature of his new form and without the support of his beloved leader, Gul\'dan, Gorefiend killed himself.$B$BIf he walks these lands now as a spirit, it is news to me. Yet, perhaps I can divine such knowledge with your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=10633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='In life, Gorefiend was a bastard, but in death, Gorefiend was an unmitigated terror.$B$BTo the southeast you will find Netherwing Ledge. What was once part of the mainland of Shadowmoon is now a floating island in the sky.$B$BVhel\'kur, spawn of Deathwing, once called it his home, but now knows it as his grave. He flies an endless circle above the island, seething at his defeat to Gorefiend.$B$BIf you are to recover the Gorefiend\'s armor, it is Vhel\'kur that you must defeat.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='I must have all of the pieces before I am able to divine the fate of Gorefiend.' WHERE `entry`=10634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='When I have all three of the pieces in my possession, I will be able to divine the whereabouts of Gorefiend.' WHERE `entry`=10635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Only with all three united may I divine the secrets you so desperately seek!' WHERE `entry`=10636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let us hope that distraction bought us the time we need to fully learn what we need of the training grounds at Karabor.' WHERE `entry`=10637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you completed the task I asked of you?' WHERE `entry`=10637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You did what? FOOL!$B$BYou must right this wrong. After all, it is your fault. Take one of these helmets. They are each infused with the ever-burning ash that you retrieved for me. More importantly, they will allow you to see the ghosts of Shadowmoon, including Teron Gorefiend.$B$BShould you ever find Teron Gorefiend, destroy him.' WHERE `entry`=10639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve come a long way, stranger. I\'m surprised whoever sent you has heard of me.' WHERE `entry`=10640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve proven you\'re not tainted by the Legion\'s touch and the enemy of my enemy is my friend.' WHERE `entry`=10641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Zorus begins to craft something out of the ash samples.>$B$BIt is done. Behold, Spectrecles!' WHERE `entry`=10642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You claim to have heard the ghosts whisper to you? And they mentioned Teron Gorefiend?$B$B<Zorus shudders.>$B$BYes... I know Teron Gorefiend. Rather, I knew of him. He has long been thought dead. What could these ghosts be speaking of?' WHERE `entry`=10643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Gorefiend? Why, I have not heard that name in ages!$B$BAfter the Second War, Gorefiend returned here, along with his death knights. Unable to cope with the terrible nature of his new form and without the support of his beloved leader, Gul\'dan, Gorefiend killed himself.$B$BIf he walks these lands now as a spirit, it is news to me. Yet, perhaps I can divine such knowledge with your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=10644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You did what? FOOL!$B$BYou must right this wrong. After all, it is your fault. Take one of these helmets. They are each infused with the ever-burning ash that you retrieved for me. More importantly, they will allow you to see the ghosts of Shadowmoon, including Teron Gorefiend.$B$BShould you ever find Teron Gorefiend, destroy him.' WHERE `entry`=10645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You know the story now. Only one thing remains to be done.' WHERE `entry`=10646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Quite da haul you got der, mon. Well done! An\' ya be getting\' yer reward. Don\'t ya worry!' WHERE `entry`=10647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yep, here\'s your reward. Don\'t go spendin\' it all in once place.' WHERE `entry`=10648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I was able to sense the book\'s power from yards away. The temptation to keep it is... very strong.' WHERE `entry`=10649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You bring this abomination of a book to this holy site? You\'d better have a very good explanation, $N?' WHERE `entry`=10650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent work, $N! Your victory over Varedis will have a tremendous impact on our war against Illidan.$B$BYou\'ve proven yourself not just to the Aldor but to all of Outland. Allow me to destroy what remains of that horrible book.' WHERE `entry`=10651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome, $C. Try not to give our position away.$B$BWe wouldn\'t last long if Kael\'s cronies sniff us out.' WHERE `entry`=10652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You continue to prove your worth, $N. Fight the enemies of the Light wherever you may find them; your actions will be well-rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=10654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You continue to prove your worth, $N. Fight the enemies of the Light wherever you may find them; your actions will be well-rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=10655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Kael\'s Sunfury army is extremely well-trained. Very impressive job, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Toshley wants you to use the Repolarized Magneto Sphere to absorb 25 lightning strikes from the Scalewing Serpents. As well, collect 5 Scalewing Lightning Glands. Then, deliver them back to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Woo hoo, it worked! To be honest I wasn\'t sure... I calculated a twenty-three point seven two chance that you\'d implode by the third strike.$B$B<Toshley grins innocently.>$B$BSo, now we know that the sphere works, we should have no problem meeting our energy needs for the Zephyrium Capacitorium. Well, that is if we can find more volunteers to go out there and get zapped.$B$BStill, you\'ve pioneered our efforts and deserve something in return!' WHERE `entry`=10657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The trick to using the repolarized magneto sphere is to know when to turn it off before you end up getting truly fried.$B$BOf course, you need to balance that against how many of those flying serpents you want to have to face.$B$BSpeaking of which, have you managed to charge up the sphere?' WHERE `entry`=10657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent! That\'ll show Kael\'thas not to underestimate our power.' WHERE `entry`=10658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Kael\'s army will soon fall.' WHERE `entry`=10659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This may take a while. Take these coins for your hard work.' WHERE `entry`=10660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Gnomus hungrily grabs at the spleens.>$B$BHere\'s your coin as promised. I\'ll call for you if I need more spleens.$B$BSo delicious... I dare say that they are \'spleendid!\'' WHERE `entry`=10661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ordinn sent you with these?$B$B<The smith examines the ingots.>$B$BHe was right. Most of the magic is gone, but I can still sense traces of it. With some work and a few \'exotic\' resources, I can forge you a powerful anti-demon sword from this metal.' WHERE `entry`=10662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The smith frowns and examines the ingots.>$B$BI\'ll be frank with you, $C. I\'m a relic of an age when cooperation with the Horde was unthinkable.$B$BI am not so blind as to see that we do not have common enemies. I will help you to reforge the anti-demon weapon but it\'s going to take a lot of hard work and a few \'exotic\' resources.' WHERE `entry`=10663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<The smith accepts the materials, nodding approvingly.>$B$BThese will suffice. The remainder of the materials I\'ll need won\'t be quite so easy to come by.' WHERE `entry`=10664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is even more potent than I expected! With this much power, I could forge a dozen blades!' WHERE `entry`=10665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<David leafs through the book\'s pages, shuddering.>$B$BThis is not something to be trifled with, $N. After the weapon is created, I will destroy it. There is enough demonic power about in the world without this text out in the open.' WHERE `entry`=10666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This should do the trick. I\'d hoped for a bit more, but to be honest, we were lucky to get our hands on any at all out here.' WHERE `entry`=10667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you\'re not with Illidan. You\'re one step closer to gaining my full trust.' WHERE `entry`=10668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done, $N. He still remembered the day I drove this spear into him?  That was so long ago...' WHERE `entry`=10669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<David Wayne holds the gem up, to the light, admiring it.>$B$BIt\'s aboslutely flawless, and that\'s exactly what we\'ll need. A flawed gem would endanger the weapon\'s wielder, twisting the magic against them.' WHERE `entry`=10670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Dizzy Dina has asked you to acquire 5 Ether-Energized Flesh and return them to her at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='These ought to do nicely. Don\'t they stink, though?$B$BI hope that this is worth your troubles... I\'m just glad that it was you collecting this stuff instead of me!' WHERE `entry`=10671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Listen, there is no time to spare. I\'ve been watching the tagged diemetradons and have discovered that they all report to a gigantic, nay, ENORMOUS, diemetradon named Felspine the Greater.' WHERE `entry`=10672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Listen, I do not have the time nor the inclination to explain what any of this means. Just tag those diemetradons.' WHERE `entry`=10672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='At last! Total protection against lava is mine! Of course you get a cut of this technology too, $N. You\'ve earned it!' WHERE `entry`=10673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Toshley would like you to use the Light Trap to catch 15 Razaani Light Orbs. Return to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains after you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hey! Wait just one damned minute!!$B$BThis doesn\'t look good...' WHERE `entry`=10674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I take it that since we\'re speaking, you have the light orbs from the Razaan\'s Landing? It\'ll be interesting to take a look at them and see what the ethereal are up to.' WHERE `entry`=10674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Toshley wants you to retrieve the Collection of Souls and return it to him at Toshley\'s Station in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Good riddance to him! Thank you for putting an end to their macabre twisting of magic and technology.$B$BAs a true hero of gnomes everywhere, I hereby bequeath unto you our highest honor... some power converters and your pick of any of these.$B$BI know that you\'ll put them to good use!' WHERE `entry`=10675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<David mops sweat from his brow.>$B$BThe bulk of the work is done, but to set the magics, the blade must now be quenched.' WHERE `entry`=10676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is fantastic but I just received some incredible news!' WHERE `entry`=10677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'ll need some alone time now, $N. Thanks for all the help!' WHERE `entry`=10678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Well done!$B$B<The smith examines the blade closely.>$B$BI\'d say it\'s a fair improvement over the crude Legion weapons you started with. Not only will this blade cut down Illidari demons, but it will work against the Legion\'s minions as well.' WHERE `entry`=10679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is good that you came, $R. We have much work to do.' WHERE `entry`=10680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It is good that you came, $R. We have much work to do.' WHERE `entry`=10681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Tree Warden Chawn has asked you to negotiate with Overseer Nuaar. Return to the tree warden at Evergrove in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains afterward.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='WHAT?!  They dismissed you and our proposals out of hand?$B$BThis is outrageous!  We go to them in good faith, and they turn you away without even trying to come to a compromise?$B$BWell, we\'ll see about that!' WHERE `entry`=10682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Is everything okay?' WHERE `entry`=10682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='It matches Akama\'s handwriting... let us see what we can learn.' WHERE `entry`=10684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes! The four fragments of the medallion. Now to put them together...' WHERE `entry`=10685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='We\'ve been expecting you, $N. Akama said you would arrive sooner or later.' WHERE `entry`=10686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Let\'s take a closer look at these weapons, $N. Hmmm... this is rather unsettling.' WHERE `entry`=10687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='That should buy us some time... hopefully it will be enough for us to obtain more information.' WHERE `entry`=10688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Have you completed the task I asked of you?' WHERE `entry`=10688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve come a long way, stranger. I\'m surprised whoever sent you has heard of me.' WHERE `entry`=10689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill Rema and then inform Commander Skyshadow at Sylvanaar in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Unbelievable. Did you slay Rema all by yourself?$B$BBy the looks of you, I\'d say that you could. You know, we\'re looking for a young, strong $C, such as yourself, to help out around here, especially with the problems we continually have with the ogres. Make sure that you follow-up with me on that possibility.$B$BWell, you\'ve definitely earned the bounty that I put on that wanted poster.$B$BPlease, take your pick.' WHERE `entry`=10690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Many would pay a great price for the book you carry with you. It is a shame we\'ll have to destroy it.' WHERE `entry`=10691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You\'ve done well, $N. By slaying Varedis you\'ve put an end to one of Illidan\'s most dangerous projects.$B$BYour name will definitely get around after this.$B$BAllow me to take what remains of the Book of Fel Names. I will make sure it\'s properly... disposed of.' WHERE `entry`=10692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Fantastic! Should I have any other grunt work that needs to be done, I\'ll find you.' WHERE `entry`=10702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Aye, good work! Here\'s some coin for your efforts. If we be needin\' more garbage taken out, I\'ll know who to call.' WHERE `entry`=10703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I am impressed, $N, though I should expect nothing less of the hero who returned the ata\'mal crystal to us.$B$BGive over the two shards and I will see to it that they are combined into their final form. Then you will have access to the Arcatraz.' WHERE `entry`=10704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The Ashtongue Seer has been long dead. As you turn over his body, you spot writing scrawled on the floor.' WHERE `entry`=10705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Yes... of course! It all becomes clear now.' WHERE `entry`=10706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='The crystal! Its power... now in my hands!' WHERE `entry`=10707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='<As you give the medallion to A\'dal, it disappears into his being in a flash of light.>$B$B<You are briefly shown a glimpse of a moment... perhaps in the future. You see Akama and Maiev coming out of the Warden\'s Cage, fighting their way to the Dark Temple. A third figure shrouded in shadows is aiding them. Upon closer inspection you notice that the figure is you.>' WHERE `entry`=10708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Return to Rexxar at Thunderlord Stronghold in Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='So my father does live. I did not expect him to forgive - that was never his way. But I had hoped that the years had dulled the anger he must have felt at my departure.$B$BThirty years ago, I left the Mok\'Nathal to follow the Horde to Azeroth. Leoroxx was staunchly against it, but then, he never gave me any reason to stay. Still, a better welcome for this I had hoped for.$B$BHe wanted a Mok\'Nathal for a son and he has one now, even if he will not know it.$B$BI must open his eyes.' WHERE `entry`=10709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Sign Tally\'s Waiver, then speak with Rally Zapnabber to use the Zephyrium Capacitorium. Return to Tally Zapnabber at Toshley\'s Station.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Wow! Again, you survived! I\'m a much better engineer than I give myself credit for!$B$BHere\'s your pay! And check back with me later... I\'ll have more experiments that\'ll need more test subjects!' WHERE `entry`=10710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Don\'t worry, Mitharan! Worry never got anyone anywhere!' WHERE `entry`=10710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, gosh! You\'re back so soon! I saw you take off and you shot up like a rocket! I was sure it would take at least a month of convalescing to mend the broken legs from that flight! You\'re tough, and brave, and foolhardy! But mostly... you\'re brave!' WHERE `entry`=10711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What? You don\'t want to perform the experiment? Don\'t fret, Domme! I\'m behind you all the way!' WHERE `entry`=10711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Speak with Rally Zapnabber to use the Zephyrium Capacitorium. While flying to Ruuan Weald, spin the Nether-weather Vane. Deliver the Spinning Nether-weather Vane to O\'Mally Zapnabber in Ruuan Weald.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, you took readings from the nether-weather vane? Splendid! The data gained from this instrument -- coupled with my measurements of druid magic -- will bear much fruit!$B$BOh, the applications will boggle the mind, I assure you!' WHERE `entry`=10712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Hello hello! My clo-... I mean, my cousin Tally told me you\'d be dropping in. Do you have something for me?' WHERE `entry`=10712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Venture out into the Ruuan Weald and slay 10 Wyrmcult Hewers, then return to Tree Warden Chawn at Evergrove in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you, $N.$B$BWhile we\'ll see to it that the wildlife will replenish itself in quick order, regrowing the trees, especially in a natural fashion, is a much more time-intensive process.' WHERE `entry`=10713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Find a Bloodmaul Taskmaster and a Bloodmaul Soothsayer engaged in conversation, then use Rexxar\'s Whistle to summon Spirit to spy on them. When this is complete, return to Rexxar at Thunderlord Village in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='<Spirit perches upon Rexxar\'s shoulder, while Rexxar listens intently.>$B$BSo it is the sons of Gruul that are behind the ogres\' actions. They command the Bloodmaul ogres to destroy the Mok\'Nathal to gain their favor.' WHERE `entry`=10714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What have you learned, $N?' WHERE `entry`=10714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Baron Sablemane has told you that in order to make the poison that Rexxar needs, you must acquire 7 Crust Burster Venom Glands. Return to him at the Circle of Blood in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains once you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Very well. A simple, if mundane, task has been completed. Now, hand me the glands and I will do the difficult part.' WHERE `entry`=10715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Samia Inkling has asked you to acquire 5 Wyrmcult Nets and return them to her at Evergrove in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Oh, those look splendid. These cultists certainly have an eye for craftsmanship.$B$BToo bad for them that it\'s misdirected.$B$BAnd now that we have the nets, would you be willing to help little old me with a thing or two?' WHERE `entry`=10717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Garm Wolfbrother has told you where the Mok\'Nathal, Rexxar\'s people, live. Speak of this to Rexxar at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='What is this you speak of?$B$BGarm Wolfbrother? He was the last chieftain of the Thunderlord clan. If you have communed with his spirit, then it must be true.' WHERE `entry`=10718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is interesting, but disturbing. I wonder if Samia knows who this Kolphis Darkscale is?' WHERE `entry`=10719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Use the Kodohide Drum at the Marmot Den. While controlling the Marmot, poison the three kegs in the Bloodmaul Camp. When that is completed, return to Rexxar at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='For many long years I have concentrated my efforts on perfecting the ways of communicating with nature. This is but a small part of the untapped potential that beasts can bring to you.' WHERE `entry`=10720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Obtain Grulloc\'s Sack and deliver it to Baron Sablemane at the Circle of Blood in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.' WHERE `entry`=10721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Gather up enough Costume Scraps from the various wyrmcultists to create an Overseer Disguise. Use the disguise to attend the meeting with Kolphis Darkscale, and report your findings back to Tree Warden Chawn at Evergrove in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Attack us? Wipe us out? I think not!$B$BThis Blackwing Coven has a great deal to learn if they think the Cenarion Expedition is so easily dealt with!$B$BWhat is it that they say? Turnabout is fair play!' WHERE `entry`=10722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What news do you bring? Do you know what the wyrmcultists are up to?' WHERE `entry`=10722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Go to Boulder\'mok and collect 3 Grisly Totems from the Boulder\'mok ogres. Use Sablemane\'s Trap at Gorgrom\'s Altar to set the trap and summon and kill Gorgrom the Dragon-Eater.$B$BWhen Gorgrom is dead, place the 3 Grisly Totems near his corpse, then return to Rexxar at Thunderlord Stronghold in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='The ogres of Bloodmaul and their master, Gorgrom, will trouble the Mok\'Nathal no longer.$B$BHowever, I worry about the effect our actions will have on the other gronn. I believe we must end this fight once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=10723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='The Bloodmaul ogres will trouble us no longer when this task is done.' WHERE `entry`=10723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc8`='Kill Bladespire ogres to get the Wyvern Cage Key. Once you have it, go to the Wyvern Cage and use Spirit\'s Whistle to summon Spirit, who will unlock the cage. After Leokk is free, return to Rexxar at Thunderlord Village in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Leokk has brought to us the head from one of the black dragons at Dragon\'s End. With this, we will be able to infuriate Goc, the gronn that captured him, and lure him into battle.' WHERE `entry`=10724;
