UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I don\'t see much of use here, but there are a couple of entries that could prove useful. It looks as though these arakkoa were preparing some kind of elaborate magical ritual up until the time of their deaths, but why? There\'s also a curious note here about a \'deserter.\'' WHERE `entry`=10760;
