UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hmm... so the left leg servo was activating the right leg?  But I saw the left leg moving...$B$BEh, details. I\'ll get to that later, but two out of three things worked: That isn\'t half bad!$B$BThanks for checking this out for me, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='I\'m waiting on those test results, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='So you found them? Why did the missing men and women not return with you? We cannot compel them to change their minds and return to their families. I will let the families know that the relatives have been found and that they are safe. After this cult is broken up, they will likely return to their normal lives.' WHERE `entry`=25293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hmm... so the bullets had quite a bit of spread?$B$BTo some people that may be a problem... me, though, I see it as a blessing in disguise!$B$BOur enemies will be running all over the place, so with a bit of a spread, the tank drivers won\'t need to lead the target!' WHERE `entry`=25295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='What\'s wrong?  Did you forget how to shoot?' WHERE `entry`=25295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Curses! We had to fall back. But Thermaplugg\'s lost, and he knows it... he\'s only bought himself time. We hold the surface, and when the radiation clears we\'ll assault and recapture Gnomeregan with a force twice this size.' WHERE `entry`=25393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='These be enough for me purposes. Now comes de hard part.' WHERE `entry`=25444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='Ya helpin\' with da frogs or not?' WHERE `entry`=25444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='$N, you\'d be a mighty warrior and a fierce commrade to da Darkspear trolls. De Echo Isles are OURS now and we couldn\'ta done it wit\'out ya.$B$BTake dis cloak. Wear it wit pride. You\'d be a member of da tribe now!$B$BIn no time, da trolls will have a home again and we have you to thank for dat.' WHERE `entry`=25445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I\'m already beginnin\' to see what de frogs are seein\'. Ya done it perfectly, $N. Now Vol\'jin and I will see what Zalazane be plannin\'.' WHERE `entry`=25446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Ya found some good ones. I be trainin\' them hard and we won\'t stop until we\'ve driven Zalazane from our islands.' WHERE `entry`=25461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc8`='We be needin\' as many volunteers as we can get.' WHERE `entry`=25461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Vanira\'s frogs be tellin\' de truth, den? Dis tiger be a druid and an ally? We couldn\'t be hopin\' for a better outcome. Dis be a good omen for de coming battle.' WHERE `entry`=25470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='I will take de spirits\' advice to heart. Wit\' dem behind us and de power of de ancient loas of de Darkspear Tribe, we be ready to reclaim what\'s ours!' WHERE `entry`=25480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='At last, everythin\' be ready. Now, we show Zalazane what happen to dose who defy de Darkspears!' WHERE `entry`=25495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='This is the speech from Toby?  Fantastic!$B$BRecruit, you\'ve done all we could possibly ask for and the Gnomeregan Army thanks you!$B$BWe\'ve got a strike team heading to Gnomeregan now and that wouldn\'t have been possible without your assistance. For all of your help, we\'d like you to join the Gnomeregan Reserves!$B$BIt doesn\'t pay very well, but you do get this snazzy helmet. Hang on to that, you might need it someday!' WHERE `entry`=25500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you for heeding Rhonin\'s call, brave adventurer. Let me share with you what we know regarding recent events, and any assistance you might offer would be greatly appreciated.' WHERE `entry`=26012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thank you again, $C, for rescuing me from Baltharus\'s clutches! There is still much work to be done, however....' WHERE `entry`=26013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`=' We owe you a debt of gratitude, mortal, for driving the invaders from the Sanctum. But this news of the Destroyer is troubling beyond words. I have much to discuss with the other members of the Accord. Take these as a token of my thanks, as you gird yourselves for the coming storm.' WHERE `entry`=26034;

